00:03:08.271 --> 00:03:11.007 position:7% line:83% align:start
[TUAREG LEADER] "Tuareg" means
"The people abandoned by God."

00:03:11.040 --> 00:03:13.843 position:27% line:83% align:start
Only enemies and
outsiders call us this.

00:03:13.876 --> 00:03:15.244 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
