00:03:25.555 --> 00:03:28.958 position:19% line:83% align:start
And most of the time,
too closely for my taste.

00:03:31.527 --> 00:03:33.963 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
They can't see us in the desert.

00:03:33.996 --> 00:03:36.731 position:19% line:83% align:start
And yet, that doesn't
mean they're not here.

00:03:44.106 --> 00:03:45.041 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
