is what you people say, yes?

00:04:21.810 --> 00:04:23.845 position:24% line:83% align:start
--[UWE chuckles]
--[SOLDIER B] Heh-heh.

00:04:23.878 --> 00:04:25.214 position:33% line:83% align:start
[SOLDIER C]
Hm? Heh.

00:04:25.248 --> 00:04:29.085 position:19% line:83% align:start
