practice what you preach.

00:04:29.118 --> 00:04:32.321 position:13% line:83% align:start
Instead, you simply impose
your way of life on others.

00:04:32.355 --> 00:04:34.390 position:27% line:89% align:start
[SOLDIERS grunt]

00:04:34.423 --> 00:04:36.259 position:24% line:83% align:start
We're not here to
"impose" anything.

00:04:36.292 --> 00:04:37.892 position:16% line:89% align:start
