I wasn't strong enough.

00:05:23.306 --> 00:05:26.875 position:5% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] I wasn't brave enough to
follow her to the other side.

00:05:28.009 --> 00:05:30.446 position:33% line:83% align:start
You and me.
Let's do it, Tuan.

00:05:30.479 --> 00:05:32.280 position:33% line:89% align:start
Die with me.

00:05:35.016 --> 00:05:38.853 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
I'm sorry, Miach.

00:05:40.356 --> 00:05:43.526 position:21% line:83% align:start
