00:05:48.531 --> 00:05:51.434 position:10% line:89% align:start
Go! Head back to the desert!

00:05:51.467 --> 00:05:53.569 position:41% line:83% align:start
[UWE]
Hurry, Tuan! We gotta go!

00:05:53.602 --> 00:05:54.570 position:27% line:83% align:start
[TUAREG LEADER]
Listen to him.

00:05:54.603 --> 00:05:56.572 position:19% line:83% align:start
There will be serious
trouble if the W.H.O.

00:05:56.605 --> 00:05:58.239 position:27% line:83% align:start
