No way we'll shake it!

00:06:24.065 --> 00:06:25.433 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:06:28.937 --> 00:06:30.939 position:21% line:89% align:start
[SOLDIER C, B grunt]

00:06:35.043 --> 00:06:36.211 position:33% line:89% align:start
[UWE grunts]

00:06:38.681 --> 00:06:41.316 position:10% line:83% align:start
