00:10:41.556 --> 00:10:42.724 position:33% line:89% align:start
[TUAN yelps]

00:10:49.631 --> 00:10:53.400 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
Our bodies, our tits...

00:10:55.202 --> 00:10:59.841 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
