Why did your WatchMe
not report this self-abuse?

00:14:38.792 --> 00:14:41.561 position:19% line:83% align:start
Oh, you know us girls
and our feminine wiles.

00:14:41.595 --> 00:14:43.997 position:10% line:83% align:start
Or should I say, those of us
who are still young enough

00:14:44.030 --> 00:14:45.765 position:33% line:83% align:start
to remember
how to use them.

00:14:45.799 --> 00:14:47.734 position:27% line:83% align:start
Don't get saucy
with me, Inspector.

00:14:47.767 --> 00:14:49.669 position:10% line:83% align:start
I don't know how you managed
to get away with this,

00:14:49.703 --> 00:14:50.737 position:10% line:89% align:start
but do your even comprehend

00:14:50.770 --> 00:14:53.874 position:13% line:83% align:start
how much your actions have
damaged this operation?

00:14:53.907 --> 00:14:55.541 position:7% line:89% align:start
They haven't, and they won't.

00:14:55.575 --> 00:14:57.644 position:16% line:83% align:start
Nothing I do could ever
tarnish this emblem

00:14:57.677 --> 00:14:59.646 position:10% line:89% align:start
or the office it stands for.

00:14:59.679 --> 00:15:02.749 position:16% line:83% align:start
Because you're not going
to tell anyone anything.

00:15:02.782 --> 00:15:03.850 position:27% line:89% align:start
[OS CARA huffs]

00:15:03.884 --> 00:15:06.052 position:7% line:83% align:start
We both know if the integrity
of Helix Inspectors

00:15:06.086 --> 00:15:09.122 position:16% line:83% align:start
is even questioned, the
W.H.O. loses all credibility

00:15:09.155 --> 00:15:12.158 position:7% line:83% align:start
and all its hard work to "heal
the world" becomes meaningless.

00:15:12.192 --> 00:15:15.695 position:16% line:83% align:start
And I highly doubt you'd
be eager to see that happen.

00:15:17.496 --> 00:15:19.431 position:33% line:89% align:start
Well played.

00:15:19.465 --> 00:15:21.835 position:7% line:83% align:start
But, don't think for a second
you get off scot-free.

00:15:21.868 --> 00:15:24.570 position:16% line:83% align:start
You will be punished for
your insubordination.

00:15:24.603 --> 00:15:27.774 position:7% line:83% align:start
Effective immediately, you are
relieved from active duty.

00:15:27.807 --> 00:15:28.875 position:27% line:89% align:start
Relieved from--?

00:15:28.909 --> 00:15:30.643 position:24% line:83% align:start
You wanna just up
and send me home?

00:15:30.676 --> 00:15:31.543 position:24% line:89% align:start
You can't do that!

00:15:31.577 --> 00:15:32.678 position:30% line:89% align:start
I already did.

00:15:32.712 --> 00:15:35.447 position:19% line:83% align:start
This is a battlefield,
not a tavern.

00:15:35.481 --> 00:15:36.816 position:13% line:89% align:start
You need to be reeducated.

00:15:36.850 --> 00:15:37.951 position:5% line:89% align:start
You've forgotten what it's like

00:15:37.984 --> 00:15:40.153 position:21% line:83% align:start
to love and be loved
by your neighbors.

00:15:40.186 --> 00:15:42.421 position:13% line:89% align:start
This is for your own good.

00:15:47.193 --> 00:15:48.494 position:35% line:89% align:start
Damn it...

00:15:48.527 --> 00:15:50.797 position:38% line:89% align:start
Japan...

00:15:50.830 --> 00:15:53.833 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] After all I'd done
to escape that gulag!

00:15:53.867 --> 00:15:56.069 position:7% line:89% align:start
As a teenager, I detested it.

00:15:56.102 --> 00:15:59.638 position:27% line:83% align:start
And Miach Mihie
hated it even more.

00:16:02.008 --> 00:16:03.809 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
I failed.

00:16:10.016 --> 00:16:11.650 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
I'm here.

00:16:11.684 --> 00:16:14.087 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm still alive.

00:16:14.120 --> 00:16:17.623 position:21% line:89% align:start
That means I failed.

00:16:17.656 --> 00:16:19.192 position:30% line:89% align:start
How powerless.

00:16:19.225 --> 00:16:22.628 position:5% line:89% align:start
How completely dependent I was.

00:16:22.661 --> 00:16:24.730 position:30% line:83% align:start
I thought all
I needed was Miach.

00:16:24.763 --> 00:16:26.598 position:5% line:89% align:start
She gave us not only her vision,

00:16:26.632 --> 00:16:29.635 position:13% line:83% align:start
but the tools, the weapons
to go through with it!

00:16:29.668 --> 00:16:31.770 position:7% line:89% align:start
If she couldn't help me do it,

00:16:31.804 --> 00:16:33.974 position:10% line:89% align:start
I knew I'd never be able to.

00:16:34.007 --> 00:16:36.276 position:7% line:89% align:start
I would be condemned to live.

00:16:36.309 --> 00:16:38.178 position:24% line:89% align:start
I was so certain.

00:16:38.211 --> 00:16:40.113 position:21% line:83% align:start
I didn't believe my
will was strong enough,

00:16:40.146 --> 00:16:42.915 position:24% line:83% align:start
that I was strong
enough on my own.

00:16:51.124 --> 00:16:54.060 position:30% line:83% align:start
[MOTHER gasps]
Tuan! You're awake!

00:16:54.094 --> 00:16:55.995 position:27% line:89% align:start
I failed again.

00:16:56.028 --> 00:16:56.895 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MOTHER]
Tuan!

00:16:56.929 --> 00:16:58.864 position:19% line:89% align:start
Tuan, can you hear me?

00:17:00.833 --> 00:17:02.901 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm here. Mommy's here.

00:17:02.935 --> 00:17:06.572 position:24% line:83% align:start
Everything's fine.
You're okay. [sobs]

00:17:06.605 --> 00:17:08.141 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm so happy.

00:17:08.174 --> 00:17:10.776 position:7% line:89% align:start
So happy we found you in time.

00:17:10.809 --> 00:17:15.681 position:21% line:89% align:start
[sobbing continues]

00:17:15.714 --> 00:17:17.816 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
And Miach?

00:17:17.850 --> 00:17:24.257 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MOTHER]
Miach, she... [whimpers]

00:17:24.290 --> 00:17:26.759 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
I see...

00:17:26.792 --> 00:17:28.894 position:30% line:89% align:start
She succeeded.

00:17:28.927 --> 00:17:31.597 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MOTHER weeping]

00:17:31.630 --> 00:17:32.765 position:30% line:89% align:start
[MOTHER gasps]

00:17:35.201 --> 00:17:36.802 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
What are you doing, Mom?

00:17:36.835 --> 00:17:37.970 position:35% line:89% align:start
Don't cry.

00:17:38.003 --> 00:17:40.039 position:27% line:89% align:start
I mean it, stop.

00:17:40.072 --> 00:17:42.308 position:7% line:89% align:start
Your tears are empty, useless.

00:17:42.342 --> 00:17:44.877 position:19% line:83% align:start
You didn't cause this.
It's not your fault.

00:17:44.910 --> 00:17:46.145 position:13% line:89% align:start
How can you feel so guilty

00:17:46.178 --> 00:17:49.114 position:13% line:83% align:start
over the death of someone
you never even met?

00:17:49.148 --> 00:17:51.317 position:21% line:83% align:start
Society has tricked
us into believing

00:17:51.351 --> 00:17:53.185 position:7% line:89% align:start
we all care about each other.

00:17:53.218 --> 00:17:56.688 position:5% line:83% align:start
It compels you to blame yourself
for not being able to stop her.

00:17:56.722 --> 00:17:59.191 position:21% line:83% align:start
Even though there's
nothing you could've done.

00:17:59.224 --> 00:18:00.893 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's not real.

00:18:00.926 --> 00:18:02.362 position:24% line:89% align:start
I can't stand it.

00:18:02.395 --> 00:18:04.229 position:27% line:89% align:start
I've had enough.

00:18:06.165 --> 00:18:07.699 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MOTHER]
Cian is gonna be okay.

00:18:07.733 --> 00:18:10.202 position:13% line:83% align:start
She's being treated at the
Emergency Ethics Center.

00:18:10.235 --> 00:18:12.805 position:21% line:83% align:start
They're taking very
good care of her there.

00:18:16.642 --> 00:18:19.812 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
I'm sorry, Miach.

00:18:26.285 --> 00:18:28.187 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
Well, I'm a goner.

00:18:41.400 --> 00:18:43.902 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
Are you guys gonna die with me?

00:18:45.003 --> 00:18:47.272 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:18:47.306 --> 00:18:49.975 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Miach was the
smartest girl I'd ever met,

00:18:50.008 --> 00:18:52.744 position:7% line:89% align:start
so thorough, so well prepared.

00:18:52.778 --> 00:18:56.682 position:10% line:83% align:start
No problem existed that she
couldn't find a solution to.

00:18:56.715 --> 00:18:58.717 position:21% line:83% align:start
I knew she'd come up
with the perfect way

00:18:58.750 --> 00:19:00.986 position:5% line:89% align:start
to strike back at the "system."

00:19:03.889 --> 00:19:04.990 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:19:07.426 --> 00:19:10.395 position:19% line:83% align:start
[MIACH] Here, I hacked
my parents' MediCare unit.

00:19:12.865 --> 00:19:13.866 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
One a day,

00:19:13.899 --> 00:19:16.001 position:16% line:83% align:start
and your body will stop
absorbing all nutrients.

00:19:16.034 --> 00:19:17.803 position:16% line:89% align:start
You'll starve to death.

00:19:21.240 --> 00:19:22.708 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Okay.

00:19:22.741 --> 00:19:24.776 position:33% line:89% align:start
[CIAN gasps]

00:19:27.846 --> 00:19:30.816 position:33% line:89% align:start
[CIAN gasps]

00:19:30.849 --> 00:19:33.685 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Cian and I were the
followers in our little cult.

00:19:33.719 --> 00:19:35.854 position:30% line:83% align:start
Miach was its
charismatic leader.

00:19:35.888 --> 00:19:38.724 position:13% line:83% align:start
She was a radical idealist
who knew too much,

00:19:38.757 --> 00:19:40.225 position:21% line:89% align:start
and hated even more.

00:19:40.259 --> 00:19:42.928 position:24% line:83% align:start
Things were always
going to come to this.

00:19:42.961 --> 00:19:44.897 position:24% line:89% align:start
It was inevitable.

00:19:49.101 --> 00:19:52.104 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
I'm sorry, Miach.

00:20:06.318 --> 00:20:10.721 position:13% line:83% align:start
[MIACH] I'm not interested
in normal people.

00:20:10.755 --> 00:20:14.493 position:10% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Miach Mihie: problem
child, juvenile delinquent,

00:20:14.526 --> 00:20:17.095 position:33% line:83% align:start
had the best
grades in our class.

00:20:17.129 --> 00:20:20.432 position:5% line:83% align:start
She kept to herself, preferring
a beautiful kind of solitude,

00:20:20.465 --> 00:20:23.435 position:10% line:83% align:start
shunning the various cliques
that invited her in.

00:20:23.468 --> 00:20:25.204 position:5% line:89% align:start
Aside from me and Cian Reikado,

00:20:25.237 --> 00:20:29.341 position:5% line:83% align:start
she never spoke to anyone unless
it was absolutely necessary.

00:20:29.374 --> 00:20:32.044 position:13% line:83% align:start
[MIACH] If you're serious
about truly isolating yourself,

00:20:32.077 --> 00:20:34.745 position:24% line:83% align:start
paper media is the
best way to do it.

00:20:34.779 --> 00:20:36.215 position:21% line:89% align:start
Movies'll work too,

00:20:36.248 --> 00:20:38.916 position:24% line:83% align:start
but nothing beats
a physical book.

00:20:38.951 --> 00:20:40.986 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Why is that?

00:20:41.019 --> 00:20:43.455 position:5% line:89% align:start
Because it's the most intimate.

00:20:43.488 --> 00:20:45.424 position:16% line:89% align:start
Just you and the pages.

00:20:45.457 --> 00:20:46.891 position:35% line:89% align:start
Isolated.

00:20:48.893 --> 00:20:52.264 position:10% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Tangible, paper books
had become all but obsolete.

00:20:52.297 --> 00:20:54.099 position:10% line:89% align:start
But that didn't deter Miach.

00:20:54.132 --> 00:20:56.435 position:16% line:83% align:start
She would download text
she wanted from the internet,

00:20:56.468 --> 00:20:58.970 position:19% line:83% align:start
take it to one of the
few remaining printers,

00:20:59.003 --> 00:21:01.073 position:24% line:83% align:start
and have them make
a physical copy.

00:21:01.106 --> 00:21:03.908 position:10% line:83% align:start
She spent her days swimming
through a vast sea of words,

00:21:03.941 --> 00:21:05.077 position:19% line:89% align:start
searching for anything

00:21:05.110 --> 00:21:07.346 position:21% line:83% align:start
that would give her
the edge she wanted.

00:21:10.482 --> 00:21:11.516 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
Given the inclination,

00:21:11.550 --> 00:21:14.219 position:13% line:83% align:start
a few people could easily
kill everyone in Japan.

00:21:14.253 --> 00:21:16.954 position:21% line:83% align:start
All they'd need are
the MediCare units.

00:21:16.988 --> 00:21:17.989 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:21:23.228 --> 00:21:24.496 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
Every home and business

00:21:24.529 --> 00:21:27.366 position:21% line:83% align:start
has at least one of
these "magic boxes."

00:21:29.167 --> 00:21:31.536 position:30% line:83% align:start
[TUAN grunts]
Miach!

00:21:34.138 --> 00:21:37.209 position:19% line:83% align:start
Say you could rig them
all to dispense poison.

00:21:41.213 --> 00:21:43.515 position:19% line:83% align:start
You'd have millions of
tiny chemical weapons

00:21:43.548 --> 00:21:46.984 position:10% line:89% align:start
in pill or injectable form.

00:21:47.018 --> 00:21:49.987 position:7% line:83% align:start
The Admedistration conditions
us to trust medicine.

00:21:50.021 --> 00:21:52.857 position:21% line:83% align:start
It makes us healthy,
makes us feel good.

00:21:52.890 --> 00:21:55.427 position:10% line:83% align:start
No one bothers wondering if
what they synthesize for us

00:21:55.460 --> 00:21:57.429 position:19% line:89% align:start
could ever be harmful.

00:21:59.531 --> 00:22:02.467 position:10% line:83% align:start
Exploiting those weaknesses
wouldn't take much.

00:22:04.068 --> 00:22:05.269 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:22:06.338 --> 00:22:07.539 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:22:13.878 --> 00:22:15.079 position:33% line:89% align:start
[TUAN gasps]

00:22:15.112 --> 00:22:18.149 position:5% line:83% align:start
Turn the system against itself,
and we overthrow the world.

00:22:36.535 --> 00:22:39.003 position:19% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Day by day, the
world becomes a healthier,

00:22:39.036 --> 00:22:42.106 position:19% line:83% align:start
safer, more beautiful
and wholesome place.

00:22:42.139 --> 00:22:44.576 position:27% line:83% align:start
Where peace and
prosperity reign supreme.

00:22:44.609 --> 00:22:49.246 position:10% line:83% align:start
So full of kindness and good
intentions, I wanna retch.

00:22:49.280 --> 00:22:50.314 position:21% line:89% align:start
I hate this country.

00:22:50.348 --> 00:22:54.251 position:13% line:83% align:start
I detest it so much, I ran
as far away as I could.

00:22:54.285 --> 00:22:56.420 position:19% line:83% align:start
But now, the prodigal
daughter has returned.

00:22:56.454 --> 00:22:57.988 position:27% line:83% align:start
[MALE ANNOUNCER]
The Tokyo Haneda Aiport

00:22:58.022 --> 00:23:00.925 position:19% line:83% align:start
has a wide variety of
medical services available.

00:23:02.493 --> 00:23:04.563 position:27% line:83% align:start
[MALE ANNOUNCER]
Relax, Take your time.

00:23:04.596 --> 00:23:06.931 position:13% line:83% align:start
And please proceed to the
nearest healthcare center

00:23:06.964 --> 00:23:08.199 position:27% line:89% align:start
at your leisure.

00:23:10.000 --> 00:23:12.303 position:10% line:83% align:start
[MALE ANNOUNCER] We hope you
enjoy your stay in Japan...

00:23:12.336 --> 00:23:14.573 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
It's all the same.

00:23:14.606 --> 00:23:18.042 position:16% line:83% align:start
Everyone looks the same,
sounds the same,

00:23:18.075 --> 00:23:20.945 position:21% line:83% align:start
does the same things
as everyone else.

00:23:20.978 --> 00:23:22.513 position:10% line:83% align:start
[MALE ANNOUNCER] ...to take
MediCare recommended supplements

00:23:22.546 --> 00:23:25.316 position:24% line:83% align:start
prior to departure
and after arrival.

00:23:28.352 --> 00:23:29.220 position:27% line:83% align:start
[MALE ANNOUNCER]
Always remember

00:23:29.253 --> 00:23:30.955 position:13% line:89% align:start
to be kind to one another.

00:23:30.988 --> 00:23:31.956 position:24% line:89% align:start
Love thy neighbor,

00:23:31.989 --> 00:23:34.125 position:24% line:83% align:start
and have goodwill
towards your fellow man...

00:23:34.158 --> 00:23:36.494 position:33% line:89% align:start
[TUAN huffs]

00:23:36.527 --> 00:23:37.495 position:24% line:83% align:start
[MALE ANNOUNCER A]
Do not forget,

00:23:37.528 --> 00:23:39.997 position:16% line:83% align:start
you are an irreplaceable
resource, and Life is...

00:23:40.030 --> 00:23:42.233 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Tuan! Tuan! Tuan, over here!

00:23:42.266 --> 00:23:44.703 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh my gosh, I was so
worried I'd missed you!

00:23:44.736 --> 00:23:46.303 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Long time no see.

00:23:46.337 --> 00:23:47.571 position:10% line:89% align:start
How'd you know I'd be here?

00:23:47.605 --> 00:23:49.039 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Well I didn't, till yesterday.

00:23:49.073 --> 00:23:50.975 position:24% line:83% align:start
But, when I found
out I was so happy,

00:23:51.008 --> 00:23:52.676 position:24% line:83% align:start
I just had to come
welcome you home!

00:23:52.711 --> 00:23:55.980 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Yeah, it all
happened kinda fast.

00:23:56.013 --> 00:23:57.715 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Cian Reikado.

00:23:57.749 --> 00:24:02.686 position:5% line:83% align:start
My old friend who agreed to die
with me thirteen years ago.

00:24:02.720 --> 00:24:05.089 position:13% line:83% align:start
[MALE ANNOUNCER A] We hope
you enjoy your stay in Japan:

00:24:05.122 --> 00:24:08.392 position:19% line:83% align:start
the land of friendship
and hospitality!

00:24:08.426 --> 00:24:10.461 position:24% line:83% align:start
All international
travelers will be scanned

00:24:10.494 --> 00:24:13.230 position:16% line:83% align:start
for infectious diseases
once you disembark.

00:24:13.264 --> 00:24:15.166 position:7% line:83% align:start
Passengers who test positive,
are asked to report...

00:24:15.199 --> 00:24:17.334 position:10% line:83% align:start
Uh, Tuan, you're attracting
a lot of attention.

00:24:17.368 --> 00:24:19.170 position:21% line:83% align:start
Maybe you shouldn't
travel in your uniform.

00:24:19.203 --> 00:24:21.038 position:7% line:89% align:start
It kinda makes you stand out.

00:24:21.071 --> 00:24:22.306 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Comes with the territory.

00:24:22.339 --> 00:24:25.042 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm a Helix Inspector,
this is what we wear.

00:24:25.075 --> 00:24:27.111 position:24% line:83% align:start
Most of my time is
spent on a battlefield.

00:24:27.144 --> 00:24:29.079 position:21% line:83% align:start
I couldn't care less
if I blend in here.

00:24:29.113 --> 00:24:31.048 position:30% line:89% align:start
[CIAN laughs]

00:24:31.081 --> 00:24:33.717 position:7% line:83% align:start
[CIAN] It must be exciting to
have such an important job!

00:24:33.751 --> 00:24:36.687 position:21% line:83% align:start
You get to help make
the world a better place!

00:24:36.720 --> 00:24:38.656 position:21% line:83% align:start
Are you going to be
staying with your parents?

00:24:38.689 --> 00:24:40.391 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Nah, I'll just find a hotel.

00:24:40.424 --> 00:24:42.126 position:21% line:89% align:start
No point going home.

00:24:42.159 --> 00:24:43.694 position:24% line:83% align:start
[CIAN] But, you've
been away for so long!

00:24:43.727 --> 00:24:46.163 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm sure everyone
will wanna see you!

00:24:46.197 --> 00:24:49.099 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Who's "everyone"?

00:24:49.133 --> 00:24:52.303 position:7% line:83% align:start
My mom gathering the neighbors
for a welcome home party?

00:24:52.336 --> 00:24:54.438 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, no thanks.

00:24:54.472 --> 00:24:55.706 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Why not?

00:24:55.739 --> 00:24:57.608 position:19% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] I wouldn't know
what to say to anyone.

00:24:57.641 --> 00:24:58.843 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
What do you mean?

00:24:58.876 --> 00:25:01.745 position:5% line:83% align:start
Tell them about your adventures
in the Sahara, or Colombia.

00:25:01.779 --> 00:25:03.980 position:24% line:83% align:start
People wanna know
what you've been up to.

00:25:05.282 --> 00:25:07.718 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] No one wants
to hear my war stories.

00:25:07.751 --> 00:25:09.687 position:21% line:83% align:start
The grim parts would
be too upsetting.

00:25:09.720 --> 00:25:12.356 position:16% line:83% align:start
And most of it's not as
exciting as you think.

00:25:12.389 --> 00:25:15.125 position:13% line:83% align:start
[CIAN] But, after all this
time, you're finally home.

00:25:15.159 --> 00:25:17.127 position:24% line:83% align:start
People need to get
to know you again,

00:25:17.161 --> 00:25:19.196 position:5% line:89% align:start
So you can rejoin the community.

00:25:19.230 --> 00:25:21.065 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] I'd rather be
on my own for a bit.

00:25:21.098 --> 00:25:22.299 position:16% line:89% align:start
What've you been up to?

00:25:22.333 --> 00:25:23.567 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Volunteering mostly.

00:25:23.601 --> 00:25:25.336 position:27% line:83% align:start
My day job isn't
anything special,

00:25:25.369 --> 00:25:27.738 position:13% line:83% align:start
so I try to donate my time
at least three days a week.

00:25:27.771 --> 00:25:32.309 position:10% line:83% align:start
Delivering meals, caring for
the elderly, stuff like that.

00:25:32.343 --> 00:25:34.178 position:13% line:83% align:start
And of course, I still go
to Morality Sessions

00:25:34.211 --> 00:25:35.713 position:24% line:83% align:start
and Health Ethics
meetings online,

00:25:35.746 --> 00:25:37.515 position:27% line:83% align:start
but that's only
15 hours a month.

00:25:37.548 --> 00:25:39.183 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh, really?

00:25:39.216 --> 00:25:40.684 position:5% line:89% align:start
You should come sometime, Tuan.

00:25:40.718 --> 00:25:42.386 position:27% line:89% align:start
They help a lot.

00:25:45.189 --> 00:25:46.122 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Are you hungry?

00:25:46.156 --> 00:25:47.324 position:13% line:89% align:start
Why don't we grab a bite?

00:25:47.358 --> 00:25:50.394 position:7% line:83% align:start
There's a new restaurant near
my place that just opened.

00:25:50.427 --> 00:25:51.462 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Just us two?

00:25:51.495 --> 00:25:52.663 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Yeah!

00:25:52.696 --> 00:25:55.064 position:10% line:83% align:start
And you can stay over after,
instead of going to a hotel.

00:25:56.600 --> 00:25:58.469 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Cian, my friend,

00:25:58.502 --> 00:26:01.572 position:7% line:83% align:start
who once tried to die with me
to rebel against this world,

00:26:01.605 --> 00:26:03.607 position:7% line:89% align:start
was now fully immersed in it.

00:26:03.641 --> 00:26:05.843 position:5% line:89% align:start
She had connected herself to it.

00:26:05.876 --> 00:26:09.145 position:10% line:83% align:start
Her WatchMe was tethered to
an Admedistration server,

00:26:09.178 --> 00:26:11.315 position:24% line:83% align:start
that told her how
to live her life.

00:26:11.348 --> 00:26:14.451 position:27% line:83% align:start
She had plunged
headfirst into adulthood.

00:26:14.485 --> 00:26:17.621 position:21% line:83% align:start
While here I stand,
stubbornly refusing to jump.

00:26:17.655 --> 00:26:19.490 position:27% line:83% align:start
Can't decide if
that's admirable,

00:26:19.523 --> 00:26:20.624 position:33% line:89% align:start
or pathetic.

00:26:20.658 --> 00:26:22.459 position:27% line:89% align:start
[gasps, grunts]

00:26:22.493 --> 00:26:24.828 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Tuan! What's wrong?

00:26:24.862 --> 00:26:26.830 position:21% line:83% align:start
Do you feel unwell,
Helix Inspector?

00:26:26.864 --> 00:26:29.533 position:13% line:83% align:start
If you'd like I'd be happy
to give you my seat.

00:26:31.267 --> 00:26:33.437 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] If I don't get the
hell out of this country fast,

00:26:33.470 --> 00:26:36.507 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll wind up slashing my
wrists or killing someone.

00:26:36.540 --> 00:26:38.409 position:10% line:89% align:start
I can't stand the kindness.

00:26:38.442 --> 00:26:40.711 position:21% line:83% align:start
But, that's not the
only reason I left.

00:26:40.744 --> 00:26:43.514 position:10% line:83% align:start
On the battlefield, I've met
all kinds of different people,

00:26:43.547 --> 00:26:45.783 position:30% line:83% align:start
from countries
all over the world.

00:26:45.816 --> 00:26:48.217 position:13% line:83% align:start
The medically standardized
population here,

00:26:48.251 --> 00:26:50.186 position:24% line:83% align:start
feels more like a
house of mirrors.

00:26:50.219 --> 00:26:51.655 position:7% line:89% align:start
Why'd you storm off like that?

00:26:51.689 --> 00:26:53.791 position:24% line:83% align:start
It was rude not to
accept her offer.

00:26:53.824 --> 00:26:56.594 position:7% line:83% align:start
With that high an S.A. score,
she might be a public official.

00:26:56.627 --> 00:26:57.795 position:30% line:89% align:start
I know, I saw.

00:26:57.828 --> 00:27:00.798 position:5% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Cian and I took different
paths after Miach's death.

00:27:00.831 --> 00:27:02.265 position:13% line:89% align:start
She let go of her defiance

00:27:02.298 --> 00:27:04.668 position:19% line:83% align:start
and conformed to what
society wanted of her.

00:27:04.702 --> 00:27:07.203 position:19% line:83% align:start
It had all been like a
rite of passage for her,

00:27:07.236 --> 00:27:10.507 position:10% line:83% align:start
a phase she grew out of and
discarded once she grew up.

00:27:10.541 --> 00:27:11.508 position:27% line:89% align:start
On the surface,

00:27:11.542 --> 00:27:13.911 position:19% line:83% align:start
it appeared as though
I'd done the same thing.

00:27:13.944 --> 00:27:16.547 position:16% line:83% align:start
I went out with friends,
got good grades.

00:27:16.580 --> 00:27:19.750 position:13% line:83% align:start
Eventually, I took Miach's
place at the head of the class.

00:27:19.783 --> 00:27:21.752 position:21% line:83% align:start
But, the whole time,
I secretly clung

00:27:21.785 --> 00:27:24.622 position:19% line:83% align:start
to the heretical ideas
she had instilled in me.

00:27:24.655 --> 00:27:25.656 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:27:38.736 --> 00:27:40.303 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Wow, this takes me back.

00:27:40.336 --> 00:27:42.640 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's been a while since
we ate lunch together.

00:27:42.673 --> 00:27:44.474 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
That it has.

00:27:49.512 --> 00:27:51.614 position:35% line:89% align:start
[giggles]

00:27:53.751 --> 00:27:57.420 position:7% line:83% align:start
Doesn't it feel weird, though?
With just the two of us?

00:27:57.453 --> 00:27:58.856 position:30% line:89% align:start
Without Miach?

00:27:58.889 --> 00:28:01.557 position:24% line:83% align:start
I guess, but she's
been gone for a while.

00:28:05.461 --> 00:28:07.731 position:13% line:83% align:start
[CIAN] She always finished
eating way before us.

00:28:07.765 --> 00:28:09.666 position:19% line:83% align:start
Then she'd make paper
airplanes just like that,

00:28:09.699 --> 00:28:11.367 position:35% line:89% align:start
Remember?

00:28:11.401 --> 00:28:13.202 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
No, I'd forgotten.

00:28:15.939 --> 00:28:19.442 position:21% line:83% align:start
[CIAN] You grew your
hair out. It's nice.

00:28:19.475 --> 00:28:21.444 position:5% line:89% align:start
Makes you look more like Miach.

00:28:24.414 --> 00:28:26.649 position:10% line:83% align:start
[CIAN] You guys already knew
each other when we met, right?

00:28:26.683 --> 00:28:29.719 position:21% line:83% align:start
Had you been friends
for a long time?

00:28:29.752 --> 00:28:33.389 position:5% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] I wouldn't say "friends."
More like she took me hostage.

00:28:33.423 --> 00:28:35.558 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
What does that mean?

00:28:35.591 --> 00:28:37.360 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
I've never told you this?

00:28:37.393 --> 00:28:39.963 position:16% line:83% align:start
One day in the park, she
just ran up and grabbed me.

00:28:39.997 --> 00:28:43.000 position:10% line:83% align:start
She wouldn't let go until I
listened to what she had to say.

00:28:43.033 --> 00:28:44.467 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Sounds like her.

00:28:44.500 --> 00:28:48.005 position:16% line:83% align:start
How she could just snare
someone in her web.

00:28:48.038 --> 00:28:49.106 position:16% line:89% align:start
Maybe when she saw you,

00:28:49.139 --> 00:28:51.641 position:10% line:83% align:start
she knew you were the friend
she'd been waiting for,

00:28:51.674 --> 00:28:53.876 position:5% line:89% align:start
and she didn't want to lose you.

00:28:53.911 --> 00:28:55.244 position:24% line:89% align:start
I don't think so.

00:28:55.278 --> 00:28:56.212 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Hm?

00:28:56.245 --> 00:28:58.781 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Miach wasn't
looking for a friend,

00:28:58.815 --> 00:29:01.617 position:24% line:83% align:start
she wanted to find
a kindred spirit.

00:29:01.651 --> 00:29:03.920 position:13% line:83% align:start
[CIAN] Aren't those pretty
much the same thing?

00:29:03.954 --> 00:29:05.321 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Not really.

00:29:05.354 --> 00:29:06.889 position:10% line:89% align:start
Friends are your companions,

00:29:06.923 --> 00:29:10.593 position:10% line:83% align:start
whereas kindred spirits are
people who share your beliefs.

00:29:10.626 --> 00:29:11.961 position:7% line:89% align:start
More like "comrades in arms,"

00:29:11.995 --> 00:29:13.997 position:24% line:83% align:start
who want to fight
for the same causes.

00:29:14.031 --> 00:29:16.332 position:10% line:89% align:start
Oh, you mean like soldiers.

00:29:16.365 --> 00:29:18.501 position:10% line:83% align:start
Guess we didn't turn out to
be what she'd hoped for,

00:29:18.534 --> 00:29:20.336 position:19% line:89% align:start
or at least I didn't.

00:29:21.738 --> 00:29:23.272 position:35% line:89% align:start
Guess not.

00:29:28.878 --> 00:29:32.782 position:21% line:83% align:start
[CIAN] Tuan, there's
something I need to tell you.

00:29:32.815 --> 00:29:35.318 position:10% line:89% align:start
I have a confession to make.

00:29:35.351 --> 00:29:36.919 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
What is it?

00:29:36.953 --> 00:29:39.589 position:16% line:83% align:start
[CIAN] I never took any
of the pills Miach gave me.

00:29:39.622 --> 00:29:42.992 position:5% line:83% align:start
I put the first one in my mouth
that day, but I didn't swallow.

00:29:43.025 --> 00:29:45.695 position:21% line:83% align:start
Then, I told my mom
and ratted you out.

00:29:47.730 --> 00:29:49.665 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
I didn't know that.

00:29:49.699 --> 00:29:53.402 position:16% line:83% align:start
[CIAN] I was too scared
to go through with it.

00:29:53.436 --> 00:29:56.339 position:10% line:89% align:start
Tuan? Aren't you mad at me?

00:29:56.372 --> 00:29:57.974 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
We were kids.

00:29:58.007 --> 00:30:01.344 position:13% line:83% align:start
I can't really blame you.
I owe you my life.

00:30:01.377 --> 00:30:03.546 position:13% line:89% align:start
Thank you for saying that,

00:30:03.579 --> 00:30:05.948 position:21% line:83% align:start
but I don't deserve
your forgiveness.

00:30:05.982 --> 00:30:09.418 position:16% line:83% align:start
I betrayed both of you,
and it still didn't save her.

00:30:09.452 --> 00:30:10.987 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
It wasn't your fault, Cian.

00:30:11.020 --> 00:30:13.689 position:30% line:83% align:start
[CIAN grunts]
It was though.

00:30:13.723 --> 00:30:15.424 position:10% line:89% align:start
I felt like I was paralyzed.

00:30:15.458 --> 00:30:18.594 position:10% line:83% align:start
I didn't take the pills, but
I didn't tell right away either.

00:30:18.628 --> 00:30:21.631 position:13% line:83% align:start
Fear overwhelmed me and I
locked myself in my room.

00:30:21.664 --> 00:30:24.901 position:5% line:83% align:start
After a few days, my mom took me
to the Emergency Ethics Center.

00:30:24.934 --> 00:30:27.036 position:16% line:83% align:start
But, before I could even
see one of the counselors,

00:30:27.069 --> 00:30:28.671 position:16% line:89% align:start
it all came pouring out.

00:30:28.704 --> 00:30:30.540 position:27% line:83% align:start
My mom told the
counselors immediately,

00:30:30.573 --> 00:30:32.074 position:24% line:83% align:start
so of course they
called your mom.

00:30:32.108 --> 00:30:34.377 position:24% line:83% align:start
They were able to
get to you in time.

00:30:34.410 --> 00:30:35.511 position:30% line:89% align:start
But not Miach.

00:30:37.079 --> 00:30:39.448 position:16% line:83% align:start
By the time anyone made
it over to check on her,

00:30:39.482 --> 00:30:40.416 position:27% line:89% align:start
it was too late.

00:30:40.449 --> 00:30:42.852 position:16% line:83% align:start
She'd been taking those
stupid pills so long

00:30:42.885 --> 00:30:44.353 position:10% line:89% align:start
that she'd become emaciated

00:30:44.387 --> 00:30:47.857 position:19% line:83% align:start
and her organs started
shutting down one by one.

00:30:47.890 --> 00:30:49.458 position:16% line:89% align:start
Her body was so damaged,

00:30:49.492 --> 00:30:52.461 position:16% line:83% align:start
they wouldn't even allow
her parents to bury her.

00:30:52.495 --> 00:30:56.799 position:16% line:83% align:start
No burial? So, then what
did they do with her body?

00:30:56.833 --> 00:30:59.135 position:16% line:83% align:start
Miach's mom told us they
donated it to science

00:30:59.168 --> 00:31:01.571 position:19% line:89% align:start
for medical research.

00:31:01.604 --> 00:31:04.774 position:10% line:83% align:start
[sniffs] Visiting her after
the funeral was hard,

00:31:04.807 --> 00:31:07.076 position:21% line:83% align:start
but I wanted to beg
her forgiveness.

00:31:07.109 --> 00:31:09.444 position:5% line:89% align:start
Maybe this is too hard for you.

00:31:09.478 --> 00:31:13.082 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
No, I want to talk about it.

00:31:13.115 --> 00:31:14.650 position:13% line:89% align:start
Even when Miach was alive,

00:31:14.684 --> 00:31:17.520 position:13% line:83% align:start
I used to wonder sometimes
why I was her friend.

00:31:17.553 --> 00:31:18.988 position:19% line:89% align:start
We were so different.

00:31:19.021 --> 00:31:22.158 position:21% line:83% align:start
Why did I wanna hang
out with her all the time?

00:31:22.191 --> 00:31:23.893 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Ever figure it out?

00:31:23.926 --> 00:31:25.628 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Strange as it sounds,

00:31:25.661 --> 00:31:28.664 position:19% line:83% align:start
I think it's because I
felt like she needed me.

00:31:28.698 --> 00:31:30.733 position:24% line:83% align:start
Not to say we had
nothing in common,

00:31:30.766 --> 00:31:32.902 position:21% line:83% align:start
I wasn't sure where
I belonged, either.

00:31:32.935 --> 00:31:34.637 position:5% line:89% align:start
And all that pressure to fit in,

00:31:34.670 --> 00:31:36.606 position:24% line:89% align:start
was just too much.

00:31:36.639 --> 00:31:37.874 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Huh.

00:31:37.907 --> 00:31:40.542 position:5% line:83% align:start
[CIAN] All I wanted was to find
a way out before it crushed me,

00:31:40.576 --> 00:31:44.579 position:5% line:83% align:start
but that wasn't enough for her.
She was determined to fight.

00:31:44.614 --> 00:31:45.848 position:7% line:89% align:start
Even though I agreed with her,

00:31:45.882 --> 00:31:49.886 position:5% line:83% align:start
I didn't think we needed to die
or kill anyone to prove a point.

00:31:49.919 --> 00:31:51.586 position:19% line:89% align:start
She lived on the edge.

00:31:51.621 --> 00:31:52.822 position:38% line:89% align:start
I know.

00:31:52.855 --> 00:31:55.825 position:10% line:83% align:start
She was always so outspoken,
always had to push the limits,

00:31:55.858 --> 00:31:58.895 position:21% line:83% align:start
which is why I felt
like she needed me.

00:31:58.928 --> 00:32:01.197 position:21% line:83% align:start
I was there to keep
her from going too far.

00:32:01.230 --> 00:32:05.101 position:19% line:83% align:start
On some level, I think
that's what she wanted.

00:32:05.134 --> 00:32:07.737 position:19% line:83% align:start
She was relying on me
to be the voice of reason

00:32:07.770 --> 00:32:08.804 position:24% line:89% align:start
and hold her back.

00:32:08.838 --> 00:32:13.109 position:21% line:83% align:start
But, when it really
mattered, I was too scared.

00:32:13.142 --> 00:32:16.711 position:10% line:83% align:start
I never realized you'd been
friends with her for her sake.

00:32:16.746 --> 00:32:18.948 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're braver than you know.

00:32:18.981 --> 00:32:20.149 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:32:28.523 --> 00:32:29.926 position:35% line:83% align:start
[WAITRESS]
More water?

00:32:35.064 --> 00:32:37.867 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

00:32:37.900 --> 00:32:40.435 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry, Miach.

00:32:56.551 --> 00:32:57.954 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:32:59.654 --> 00:33:02.158 position:21% line:89% align:start
[WAITRESS whimpers]

00:33:02.191 --> 00:33:03.758 position:30% line:89% align:start
[CIAN groans]

00:33:05.161 --> 00:33:07.229 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:33:07.263 --> 00:33:10.565 position:19% line:89% align:start
[CIAN groans, grunts]

00:33:12.034 --> 00:33:13.635 position:30% line:89% align:start
[CIAN gurgles

00:33:13.668 --> 00:33:15.104 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:33:17.073 --> 00:33:20.242 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Miach...

00:33:20.276 --> 00:33:23.112 position:27% line:89% align:start
...I'm sorry...

00:33:23.145 --> 00:33:30.052 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'm sorr-- I'm sorry, Miach...

00:33:47.203 --> 00:33:49.904 position:27% line:83% align:start
[MALE OFFICER A]
Disgraceful!

00:33:49.938 --> 00:33:53.875 position:16% line:83% align:start
[MALE OFFICER B] It's an
affront to Lifeism itself!

00:33:53.908 --> 00:33:57.846 position:7% line:83% align:start
[MALE OFFICER C] Currently, we
have nearly 2800 confirmed dead,

00:33:57.879 --> 00:33:59.781 position:10% line:89% align:start
but that number could climb.

00:33:59.814 --> 00:34:02.984 position:7% line:89% align:start
At the exact same moment, 6582

00:34:03.018 --> 00:34:05.754 position:19% line:83% align:start
people simultaneously
attempted suicide.

00:34:05.787 --> 00:34:09.724 position:7% line:89% align:start
2796 of them were successful.

00:34:09.758 --> 00:34:11.893 position:16% line:83% align:start
Eight hours and counting
since the event.

00:34:11.926 --> 00:34:14.696 position:13% line:83% align:start
Dozens remain hospitalized
in critical condition.

00:34:14.729 --> 00:34:18.033 position:19% line:83% align:start
Final death toll could
be well over 3,000.

00:34:21.603 --> 00:34:22.704 position:24% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE OFFICER A]
No common method

00:34:22.737 --> 00:34:25.874 position:19% line:83% align:start
or other recognizable
pattern links these incidents.

00:34:29.944 --> 00:34:31.713 position:10% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE OFFICER A] However,
over half of those involved

00:34:31.746 --> 00:34:34.015 position:19% line:83% align:start
were wearing augmented
contact lenses at the time.

00:34:34.049 --> 00:34:36.684 position:16% line:83% align:start
Those visual feeds have
been uploaded to the server.

00:34:36.718 --> 00:34:39.254 position:7% line:89% align:start
We're analyzing the data now.

00:34:39.288 --> 00:34:44.292 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ICHIRO panting]

00:34:54.769 --> 00:34:59.774 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ICHIRO grunting]

00:35:13.254 --> 00:35:16.724 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ICHIRO grunts]

00:35:18.960 --> 00:35:21.796 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ICHIRO gasps]

00:35:24.432 --> 00:35:29.637 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ICHIRO panting]

00:35:34.776 --> 00:35:41.049 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ICHIRO gruting]

00:35:42.183 --> 00:35:43.985 position:27% line:89% align:start
[OFFICERS gasp]

00:35:45.253 --> 00:35:48.056 position:13% line:83% align:start
This--This is a terrorist
attack at the very

00:35:48.089 --> 00:35:51.126 position:19% line:89% align:start
foundation of Lifeism!

00:35:51.159 --> 00:35:53.962 position:21% line:83% align:start
What's the condition
of the survivors?

00:35:53.995 --> 00:35:55.730 position:13% line:83% align:start
[MALE OFFICER C] Those who
did not perish immediately,

00:35:55.763 --> 00:35:58.233 position:21% line:83% align:start
have fallen into an
irreversible comatose state.

00:35:58.266 --> 00:36:01.169 position:5% line:83% align:start
We are so far unable to question
them about what they did,

00:36:01.202 --> 00:36:02.837 position:38% line:89% align:start
or why.

00:36:05.773 --> 00:36:08.443 position:10% line:83% align:start
As of this moment, the Helix
Inspection Agency officially

00:36:08.476 --> 00:36:10.712 position:16% line:83% align:start
classifies this incident
as a criminal attack

00:36:10.745 --> 00:36:12.447 position:5% line:89% align:start
against Admedistrative society!

00:36:12.480 --> 00:36:15.383 position:16% line:83% align:start
We will investigate and
find those responsible.

00:36:15.416 --> 00:36:16.484 position:30% line:89% align:start
In two hours,

00:36:16.518 --> 00:36:20.421 position:10% line:83% align:start
an emergency W.H.O. meeting
will convene in Geneva.

00:36:20.455 --> 00:36:22.857 position:7% line:83% align:start
Each of you should be familiar
with the treaties between

00:36:22.891 --> 00:36:26.127 position:5% line:83% align:start
the W.H.O., and your respective
Admedistration territories.

00:36:26.161 --> 00:36:28.963 position:16% line:83% align:start
Now is the time to make
them honor those treaties.

00:36:28.997 --> 00:36:29.998 position:21% line:89% align:start
Take the initiative.

00:36:30.031 --> 00:36:32.467 position:13% line:83% align:start
Show the world this office
will not sit idly by

00:36:32.500 --> 00:36:34.903 position:16% line:83% align:start
while someone threatens
our way of life!

00:36:43.077 --> 00:36:46.080 position:30% line:89% align:start
[TUAN grunts]

00:36:51.886 --> 00:36:54.255 position:24% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Why are you
calling on a secure line?

00:36:54.289 --> 00:36:56.291 position:7% line:83% align:start
[OS CARA] Not only was one of
the victims a friend of yours,

00:36:56.324 --> 00:36:57.959 position:21% line:83% align:start
but she did it right
in front of you.

00:36:57.992 --> 00:37:00.995 position:33% line:83% align:start
You've been
emotionally traumatized.

00:37:01.029 --> 00:37:02.796 position:24% line:83% align:start
Procedure dictates
you be suspended

00:37:02.829 --> 00:37:04.132 position:33% line:83% align:start
until you've
received drug therapy

00:37:04.165 --> 00:37:06.434 position:27% line:83% align:start
and at least 100
hours counseling.

00:37:06.467 --> 00:37:09.103 position:21% line:83% align:start
You really think I'm
traumatized? Hmph.

00:37:09.137 --> 00:37:11.272 position:13% line:83% align:start
'Cause it sounds more like
you're trying to find a way

00:37:11.306 --> 00:37:14.342 position:5% line:83% align:start
to keep me off this case, and I
don't think you wanna do that.

00:37:14.375 --> 00:37:16.277 position:21% line:83% align:start
If you did, I might
have to go to the press

00:37:16.311 --> 00:37:17.512 position:13% line:89% align:start
and tell them about Niger.

00:37:17.545 --> 00:37:19.913 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm sure they'd love to hear
about our troops' consumption

00:37:19.948 --> 00:37:22.183 position:19% line:89% align:start
of illegal substances.

00:37:22.217 --> 00:37:24.085 position:19% line:89% align:start
You cannot be serious.

00:37:24.118 --> 00:37:26.287 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Oh, I am deadly serious.

00:37:26.321 --> 00:37:29.357 position:10% line:83% align:start
When it comes to blackmail,
I don't screw around.

00:37:29.390 --> 00:37:30.525 position:38% line:89% align:start
[growls]

00:37:30.558 --> 00:37:33.228 position:13% line:83% align:start
Besides, Helix Inspectors
who witness traumatic events

00:37:33.261 --> 00:37:35.896 position:13% line:83% align:start
in the field, can be given
a reprieve before reporting

00:37:35.929 --> 00:37:40.068 position:7% line:83% align:start
for mandatory therapy in order
to complete their missions.

00:37:40.101 --> 00:37:44.205 position:10% line:83% align:start
The only condition is that a
Chief Inspector sign off on it.

00:37:47.275 --> 00:37:51.179 position:5% line:83% align:start
All right, I shall approve your
request for a five day reprieve.

00:37:51.212 --> 00:37:52.280 position:27% line:89% align:start
But understand,

00:37:52.313 --> 00:37:54.915 position:10% line:83% align:start
this will grant you nothing
beyond a brief delay.

00:37:54.948 --> 00:37:58.386 position:13% line:83% align:start
Not even I have the power
to do more than that.

00:38:03.890 --> 00:38:07.060 position:19% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] What if I never
returned to Japan?

00:38:07.094 --> 00:38:10.398 position:21% line:83% align:start
What if I never went
to lunch with Cian?

00:38:10.431 --> 00:38:12.966 position:21% line:83% align:start
Would she still have
taken her own life?

00:38:17.004 --> 00:38:20.241 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Miach once said something like,

00:38:20.275 --> 00:38:24.077 position:10% line:83% align:start
"Anyone can kill themselves,
Or kill someone else.

00:38:24.111 --> 00:38:27.215 position:24% line:83% align:start
It only depends on
whether they have the will.

00:38:27.248 --> 00:38:29.284 position:19% line:83% align:start
People hold the power
to destroy things

00:38:29.317 --> 00:38:32.387 position:21% line:83% align:start
even more important
than life," she said.

00:38:32.420 --> 00:38:35.456 position:21% line:83% align:start
Only, she never told
us what that meant.

00:38:35.490 --> 00:38:39.594 position:19% line:83% align:start
All these years later,
did Cian figure it out?

00:38:39.627 --> 00:38:44.332 position:21% line:83% align:start
Did she do this just
to prove Miach right?

00:38:44.365 --> 00:38:47.267 position:21% line:83% align:start
Whatever they knew,
they took it with them,

00:38:47.302 --> 00:38:49.604 position:21% line:89% align:start
and left me behind.

00:38:49.637 --> 00:38:50.772 position:35% line:89% align:start
Five days.

00:38:50.804 --> 00:38:54.875 position:13% line:83% align:start
That's all the time I have
to figure out why Cian died.

00:38:54.908 --> 00:38:56.143 position:21% line:89% align:start
I hope it's enough.

00:38:56.176 --> 00:39:00.581 position:7% line:83% align:start
I never realized you had been
friends with her for her sake.

00:39:00.615 --> 00:39:02.916 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're braver than you know.

00:39:17.998 --> 00:39:21.068 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
I'm sorry, Miach.

00:39:24.572 --> 00:39:35.616 position:30% line:89% align:start
[CIAN gasping]

00:39:35.650 --> 00:39:38.285 position:16% line:89% align:start
[CIAN rasping, gurgling]

00:39:38.318 --> 00:39:39.986 position:27% line:89% align:start
[WAITRESS gasps]

00:39:40.020 --> 00:39:42.356 position:30% line:89% align:start
[CIAN grunts]

00:39:42.389 --> 00:39:44.091 position:35% line:89% align:start
[thudding]

00:39:44.124 --> 00:39:46.493 position:30% line:89% align:start
[CIAN gurgles]

00:39:46.527 --> 00:39:50.997 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
Miach... I-I'm sorry.

00:39:51.031 --> 00:39:53.066 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorr--

00:39:56.436 --> 00:39:58.004 position:33% line:89% align:start
[TUAN huffs]

00:40:03.243 --> 00:40:06.947 position:41% line:83% align:start
[CIAN]
I'm sorry, Miach...

00:40:14.955 --> 00:40:16.523 position:21% line:83% align:start
[A.I.] Approximately
one month after the death

00:40:16.556 --> 00:40:19.326 position:16% line:83% align:start
of their only daughter,
the Mihie family was relocated

00:40:19.359 --> 00:40:21.128 position:10% line:89% align:start
to the Fifth Tama District.

00:40:21.161 --> 00:40:23.330 position:19% line:83% align:start
Activate "Information
Isolation Mode".

00:40:23.363 --> 00:40:25.298 position:13% line:89% align:start
Authorization: Tuan Kirie.

00:40:25.332 --> 00:40:26.633 position:41% line:83% align:start
[A.I.]
Authorization Accepted.

00:40:26.666 --> 00:40:29.136 position:16% line:83% align:start
Profile data for Senior
Inspector Tuan Kirie,

00:40:29.169 --> 00:40:32.506 position:13% line:83% align:start
will display only to those
with at least Level 5 clearance.

00:40:32.539 --> 00:40:35.242 position:19% line:83% align:start
Fifteen minutes until
arrival at Mihie residence.

00:40:35.275 --> 00:40:38.044 position:19% line:83% align:start
WatchMe data indicates
Reiko Mihie is at home.

00:40:38.078 --> 00:40:40.547 position:10% line:83% align:start
With Isolation Mode engaged,
she will not be notified of

00:40:40.580 --> 00:40:43.216 position:24% line:83% align:start
Inspector Kirie's
impending visit.

00:40:56.396 --> 00:40:58.098 position:24% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Back then,
it hadn't occurred to me

00:40:58.131 --> 00:41:00.400 position:27% line:83% align:start
to wonder about
Miach's parents.

00:41:00.434 --> 00:41:02.002 position:24% line:83% align:start
We never met each
other's families,

00:41:02.035 --> 00:41:04.004 position:13% line:89% align:start
or even talked about them.

00:41:04.037 --> 00:41:06.339 position:7% line:89% align:start
It just never mattered to us.

00:41:23.256 --> 00:41:24.724 position:21% line:89% align:start
Throughout history,

00:41:24.758 --> 00:41:27.527 position:10% line:83% align:start
people have made a habit of
letting outside influences

00:41:27.561 --> 00:41:29.029 position:21% line:89% align:start
control their lives.

00:41:29.062 --> 00:41:32.032 position:27% line:83% align:start
Their families,
careers, religion.

00:41:32.065 --> 00:41:36.269 position:5% line:89% align:start
And perhaps worst of all, money.

00:41:36.303 --> 00:41:40.207 position:10% line:83% align:start
Yet money used to be made of
nothing more than flimsy paper.

00:41:40.240 --> 00:41:41.441 position:10% line:89% align:start
Back then, people would say,

00:41:41.475 --> 00:41:45.345 position:10% line:83% align:start
"Money can't buy happiness,"
but no one actually believed it.

00:41:45.378 --> 00:41:48.482 position:24% line:83% align:start
Money's sent many
great nations to war.

00:41:48.515 --> 00:41:51.418 position:19% line:83% align:start
Money's made women and
girls sell their bodies.

00:41:51.451 --> 00:41:56.122 position:7% line:83% align:start
Nearly all aspects of everyday
life somehow revolved around it.

00:41:57.757 --> 00:42:02.195 position:5% line:83% align:start
[MIACH] But, WatchMe is far more
dangerous than money ever was.

00:42:02.229 --> 00:42:03.797 position:10% line:89% align:start
It permeates our every cell,

00:42:03.830 --> 00:42:06.233 position:24% line:83% align:start
holding our bodies
as its hostage.

00:42:06.266 --> 00:42:07.234 position:21% line:89% align:start
And in the process,

00:42:07.267 --> 00:42:10.670 position:16% line:83% align:start
it robs us of something
that money never could.

00:42:15.308 --> 00:42:17.511 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] What kind of
people are Miach's parents,

00:42:17.544 --> 00:42:19.679 position:27% line:83% align:start
to have raised a
daughter like that?

00:42:19.713 --> 00:42:23.149 position:16% line:83% align:start
A girl who romanticized
the downfall of humanity,

00:42:23.183 --> 00:42:24.618 position:21% line:83% align:start
who delighted at how
easy it would be

00:42:24.651 --> 00:42:27.454 position:7% line:89% align:start
to poison thousands of people.

00:42:40.099 --> 00:42:42.502 position:38% line:83% align:start
[REIKO]
Yes? How may I help you?

00:42:42.536 --> 00:42:45.104 position:24% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] I'm a Helix
Inspector with the W.H.O.

00:42:45.137 --> 00:42:47.206 position:21% line:83% align:start
We're investigating
yesterday's mass suicides,

00:42:47.240 --> 00:42:49.141 position:13% line:83% align:start
and I was hoping you could
answer some questions--

00:42:49.174 --> 00:42:50.377 position:38% line:83% align:start
[REIKO]
Such a tragedy.

00:42:50.410 --> 00:42:52.077 position:21% line:83% align:start
I heard about it on
the news this morning,

00:42:52.111 --> 00:42:52.879 position:16% line:89% align:start
but what's that got to--

00:42:52.913 --> 00:42:55.749 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
It's about your daughter.

00:42:55.782 --> 00:42:57.182 position:38% line:83% align:start
[REIKO]
I don't understand.

00:42:57.216 --> 00:42:59.352 position:27% line:83% align:start
She passed away
over ten years ago.

00:42:59.386 --> 00:43:00.620 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
I'm aware.

00:43:00.654 --> 00:43:04.123 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'd like to ask you about what
she was like before her death.

00:43:04.156 --> 00:43:05.492 position:38% line:83% align:start
[REIKO]
Before?

00:43:06.793 --> 00:43:09.128 position:38% line:83% align:start
[REIKO]
All right, please come in.

00:43:10.430 --> 00:43:12.097 position:38% line:83% align:start
[REIKO]
It's not a pleasant story.

00:43:12.131 --> 00:43:15.368 position:7% line:83% align:start
She tried to kill herself many
times before she succeeded.

00:43:15.402 --> 00:43:19.606 position:10% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Yes, our records show
she made prior attempts.

00:43:19.639 --> 00:43:21.307 position:7% line:89% align:start
Miach was beyond our control.

00:43:21.340 --> 00:43:25.110 position:24% line:83% align:start
She was incredibly
strong-willed and clever.

00:43:25.144 --> 00:43:27.313 position:19% line:83% align:start
However, she was also
a sensitive child.

00:43:27.346 --> 00:43:29.148 position:5% line:89% align:start
A delicate, fragile little girl

00:43:29.181 --> 00:43:31.651 position:21% line:83% align:start
we loved as much as
we possibly could.

00:43:31.685 --> 00:43:34.487 position:13% line:83% align:start
When she came to us, they
said that would be enough.

00:43:34.521 --> 00:43:35.889 position:33% line:89% align:start
Came to you?

00:43:35.922 --> 00:43:39.124 position:24% line:83% align:start
We adopted Miach.
When she was eight.

00:43:39.158 --> 00:43:40.594 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:43:41.628 --> 00:43:42.829 position:27% line:89% align:start
She was adopted?

00:43:42.862 --> 00:43:44.698 position:13% line:89% align:start
That's not in her records.

00:43:44.731 --> 00:43:46.566 position:24% line:83% align:start
The Admedistration
had launched a campaign

00:43:46.600 --> 00:43:48.367 position:27% line:83% align:start
urging childless
couples to adopt.

00:43:48.400 --> 00:43:50.770 position:16% line:83% align:start
Perhaps you remember the
conflict in Chechnya?

00:43:50.804 --> 00:43:51.605 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Of course.

00:43:51.638 --> 00:43:54.139 position:21% line:83% align:start
Conditions are still
horrible there.

00:43:54.173 --> 00:43:55.140 position:10% line:89% align:start
The day we brought her home,

00:43:55.174 --> 00:43:56.910 position:19% line:83% align:start
they told us she came
from an ethnic minority

00:43:56.943 --> 00:44:00.512 position:10% line:83% align:start
in the region and that she'd
been found in a refugee camp.

00:44:00.547 --> 00:44:02.481 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
She was a war orphan.

00:44:02.514 --> 00:44:04.483 position:38% line:83% align:start
[REIKO]
They gave us few other details.

00:44:04.516 --> 00:44:07.186 position:7% line:83% align:start
All they said was she had been
through some truly horrific

00:44:07.219 --> 00:44:09.856 position:24% line:89% align:start
experiences there.

00:44:09.889 --> 00:44:10.857 position:16% line:89% align:start
Long before we got her,

00:44:10.890 --> 00:44:14.594 position:16% line:83% align:start
she'd already undergone
intense trauma therapy.

00:44:14.628 --> 00:44:16.528 position:27% line:83% align:start
However, because
she was so young,

00:44:16.562 --> 00:44:19.298 position:7% line:83% align:start
the doctors believed she could
still grow up to be a productive

00:44:19.331 --> 00:44:24.203 position:5% line:83% align:start
member of society. That all she
needed was a warm, loving home.

00:44:24.236 --> 00:44:29.174 position:7% line:83% align:start
They said it would be enough,
but they were wrong. [sobs]

00:44:29.208 --> 00:44:31.176 position:21% line:83% align:start
Time and time again
we stopped her

00:44:31.210 --> 00:44:33.212 position:5% line:89% align:start
and sent her back to treatment.

00:44:33.245 --> 00:44:34.814 position:21% line:89% align:start
She was determined.

00:44:34.848 --> 00:44:37.616 position:10% line:89% align:start
Eventually, she found a way.

00:44:37.650 --> 00:44:38.852 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
I never knew Miach carried

00:44:38.885 --> 00:44:41.921 position:27% line:83% align:start
such a profound
darkness inside her.

00:44:41.955 --> 00:44:44.623 position:21% line:83% align:start
It wasn't something
she shared with me.

00:44:44.657 --> 00:44:45.792 position:27% line:83% align:start
After all she'd
been through,

00:44:45.825 --> 00:44:49.561 position:13% line:83% align:start
that she could still hate
Japan so much spoke volumes.

00:44:49.595 --> 00:44:52.264 position:16% line:83% align:start
She was a child of war,
yet, it was like

00:44:52.297 --> 00:44:55.467 position:10% line:83% align:start
she preferred that true hell
to this false heaven.

00:44:57.336 --> 00:44:59.839 position:5% line:83% align:start
[REIKO] The doctors recommended
we get rid of anything she had

00:44:59.873 --> 00:45:02.942 position:19% line:83% align:start
that might remind her
of her former life.

00:45:02.976 --> 00:45:07.212 position:13% line:83% align:start
But, I just couldn't bring
myself to throw that away.

00:45:10.416 --> 00:45:11.450 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:45:15.754 --> 00:45:18.357 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
Ever seen a business card?

00:45:18.390 --> 00:45:21.393 position:16% line:83% align:start
People used to use these
to share information.

00:45:21.427 --> 00:45:24.830 position:24% line:83% align:start
But only with who
they wanted to.

00:45:24.864 --> 00:45:27.232 position:16% line:89% align:start
The picture is our logo.

00:45:27.266 --> 00:45:28.434 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's so cute!

00:45:28.467 --> 00:45:29.702 position:35% line:89% align:start
I like it!

00:45:29.735 --> 00:45:31.470 position:21% line:89% align:start
[TUAN, CIAN giggle]

00:45:33.872 --> 00:45:35.674 position:7% line:89% align:start
May I ask about Miach's body?

00:45:35.708 --> 00:45:38.444 position:10% line:83% align:start
Her death certificate lists
no place of interment.

00:45:38.477 --> 00:45:40.612 position:7% line:89% align:start
Was she returned to Chechnya?

00:45:40.646 --> 00:45:42.614 position:27% line:83% align:start
No, a researcher
from a university

00:45:42.648 --> 00:45:45.417 position:24% line:83% align:start
asked if he could
have her remains.

00:45:45.451 --> 00:45:46.518 position:19% line:89% align:start
Just before she died,

00:45:46.552 --> 00:45:49.321 position:19% line:83% align:start
she said she wanted to
donate her body to science.

00:45:49.354 --> 00:45:51.423 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Who was this researcher?

00:45:51.457 --> 00:45:53.592 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm afraid I can't help you.
I don't know his name.

00:45:53.625 --> 00:45:55.861 position:5% line:89% align:start
We never had any direct contact.

00:45:55.894 --> 00:45:58.530 position:13% line:83% align:start
This is an investigation,
so I need to know.

00:45:58.564 --> 00:46:00.365 position:27% line:83% align:start
And my authority
as a Helix Inspector

00:46:00.399 --> 00:46:02.868 position:21% line:83% align:start
allows me to access
confidential information.

00:46:02.901 --> 00:46:04.002 position:19% line:89% align:start
So, if you don't mind,

00:46:04.037 --> 00:46:05.404 position:7% line:89% align:start
this will just take a moment.

00:46:05.437 --> 00:46:06.605 position:30% line:89% align:start
[REIKO gasps]

00:46:19.718 --> 00:46:21.320 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:46:21.353 --> 00:46:23.055 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Keita Saeki?

00:46:23.088 --> 00:46:25.824 position:10% line:83% align:start
His theoretical research on
pharmacology and Medicules

00:46:25.858 --> 00:46:27.960 position:13% line:89% align:start
was the basis for WatchMe.

00:46:30.662 --> 00:46:32.831 position:10% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] And the man who used
to call himself my father,

00:46:32.865 --> 00:46:35.834 position:24% line:83% align:start
Nuada Kirie, once
worked in his lab.

00:46:35.868 --> 00:46:39.371 position:7% line:83% align:start
He walked out on us, never to
be seen or heard from again.

00:46:39.404 --> 00:46:40.639 position:21% line:89% align:start
Thirteen years ago.

00:46:40.672 --> 00:46:45.010 position:7% line:83% align:start
Immediately after, I tried to
die alongside my two friends.

00:46:47.780 --> 00:46:48.981 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KEITA]
Please, come in.

00:46:49.014 --> 00:46:50.949 position:16% line:89% align:start
I've been expecting you.

00:46:51.984 --> 00:46:53.852 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Thank you for
seeing me, Professor.

00:46:53.886 --> 00:46:55.487 position:21% line:89% align:start
You're looking well.

00:46:55.521 --> 00:46:57.856 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KEITA] Looking well is a
given in this day and age.

00:46:57.890 --> 00:47:00.492 position:5% line:89% align:start
Thanks to WatchMe, who doesn't?

00:47:00.526 --> 00:47:01.727 position:10% line:89% align:start
The once harsh realities of

00:47:01.760 --> 00:47:04.062 position:19% line:83% align:start
illness and aging are
things of the past.

00:47:04.096 --> 00:47:06.498 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] It's an antiquated
turn of phrase, perhaps,

00:47:06.532 --> 00:47:08.033 position:16% line:83% align:start
but it's something I've
always wanted to say

00:47:08.066 --> 00:47:09.701 position:13% line:89% align:start
to the father of WatchMe.

00:47:09.735 --> 00:47:12.004 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KEITA] I never imagined a
voraciously health-conscious

00:47:12.037 --> 00:47:14.907 position:24% line:83% align:start
society would use
it the way it has,

00:47:14.940 --> 00:47:16.775 position:24% line:83% align:start
but the Maelstrom
changed everything.

00:47:16.809 --> 00:47:18.877 position:24% line:83% align:start
The result is the
world we now live in.

00:47:18.911 --> 00:47:19.912 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
What do you mean?

00:47:19.945 --> 00:47:22.781 position:21% line:83% align:start
People didn't always
want this kind of future?

00:47:22.815 --> 00:47:24.550 position:19% line:83% align:start
[KEITA] What happened
over 50 years ago,

00:47:24.583 --> 00:47:27.519 position:24% line:83% align:start
was a cataclysm of
apocalyptic proportions.

00:47:27.553 --> 00:47:30.956 position:10% line:83% align:start
More than ten million lives
lost in North America alone.

00:47:30.989 --> 00:47:33.392 position:19% line:83% align:start
The chaos and nuclear
war that followed

00:47:33.425 --> 00:47:34.960 position:10% line:89% align:start
nearly destroyed the planet.

00:47:34.993 --> 00:47:38.564 position:19% line:83% align:start
There was violence and
terrorism on a global scale.

00:47:38.597 --> 00:47:41.500 position:13% line:83% align:start
Fear reigned supreme, and
the world as we know it,

00:47:41.533 --> 00:47:43.669 position:27% line:83% align:start
with its WatchMe
and Admedistrations,

00:47:43.702 --> 00:47:45.804 position:19% line:89% align:start
was born of that fear.

00:47:45.838 --> 00:47:49.007 position:21% line:83% align:start
A fear that's never
fully gone away.

00:47:49.041 --> 00:47:52.410 position:13% line:83% align:start
But I'm certain you didn't
come here for a history lesson.

00:47:52.443 --> 00:47:54.746 position:19% line:83% align:start
So, what can I do for
you, Helix Inspector?

00:47:54.780 --> 00:47:57.816 position:19% line:83% align:start
I assume this is about
yesterday's mass suicides?

00:47:57.850 --> 00:48:00.919 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's about Miach Mihie.

00:48:00.953 --> 00:48:03.755 position:16% line:83% align:start
You took custody of her
remains after her death.

00:48:05.657 --> 00:48:08.994 position:16% line:83% align:start
Her body was supposed to
be delivered to this lab,

00:48:09.027 --> 00:48:10.229 position:30% line:89% align:start
but it wasn't.

00:48:10.262 --> 00:48:13.131 position:7% line:83% align:start
All specimens passing through
this facility get processed

00:48:13.165 --> 00:48:16.902 position:24% line:83% align:start
and cataloged, yet
there's no record of her.

00:48:16.935 --> 00:48:18.770 position:27% line:89% align:start
The reason why?

00:48:18.804 --> 00:48:20.973 position:21% line:83% align:start
You didn't actually
take Miach's body!

00:48:21.006 --> 00:48:23.775 position:21% line:83% align:start
However, my father,
Nuada Kirie, did!

00:48:23.809 --> 00:48:25.978 position:10% line:83% align:start
Hold on, now. When did your
father come in to this?

00:48:26.011 --> 00:48:27.713 position:10% line:89% align:start
I don't have time for games.

00:48:27.746 --> 00:48:28.780 position:24% line:89% align:start
Tell me the truth.

00:48:28.814 --> 00:48:30.849 position:19% line:83% align:start
Where did he take her,
what did he want with her,

00:48:30.883 --> 00:48:35.486 position:10% line:83% align:start
and is any of this connected
to what happened yesterday?

00:48:35.519 --> 00:48:37.956 position:16% line:83% align:start
Fine. I'll get a warrant
if that's what it takes.

00:48:37.990 --> 00:48:40.859 position:16% line:83% align:start
Nuada's little girl grew
into a real ball breaker.

00:48:40.893 --> 00:48:41.827 position:30% line:89% align:start
He'd be proud.

00:48:41.860 --> 00:48:44.528 position:19% line:83% align:start
Wouldn't know. It's an
occupational hazard,

00:48:44.562 --> 00:48:47.099 position:13% line:83% align:start
though I've been known to
break more than just balls.

00:48:48.566 --> 00:48:51.003 position:30% line:83% align:start
[KEITA sighs]
He's in Baghdad.

00:48:51.036 --> 00:48:54.973 position:13% line:83% align:start
At one of the labs of the
SEC Neuroscience Consortium.

00:48:55.007 --> 00:48:58.010 position:16% line:83% align:start
My one-time student has
now surpassed his teacher.

00:48:58.043 --> 00:49:00.678 position:24% line:83% align:start
He moved on to far
more advanced research.

00:49:00.711 --> 00:49:02.580 position:24% line:83% align:start
The two of us have
had no communication

00:49:02.613 --> 00:49:04.482 position:19% line:89% align:start
since the day he left.

00:49:04.515 --> 00:49:07.152 position:16% line:89% align:start
What was he researching?

00:49:07.185 --> 00:49:09.187 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KEITA] A few years back,
a Russian scientist

00:49:09.221 --> 00:49:11.990 position:13% line:83% align:start
published a groundbreaking
thesis on the mesencephalon

00:49:12.024 --> 00:49:15.760 position:16% line:83% align:start
and how its neurological
synapses affect human will.

00:49:15.794 --> 00:49:18.596 position:13% line:83% align:start
Sounds rather complicated,
but in layman's terms,

00:49:18.629 --> 00:49:21.799 position:13% line:83% align:start
it's simply the theory of
"why we do what we do."

00:49:21.833 --> 00:49:25.103 position:19% line:83% align:start
This area here is the
mesencephalon, or midbrain.

00:49:25.137 --> 00:49:27.538 position:19% line:83% align:start
Sometimes known as the
mind's reward center,

00:49:27.571 --> 00:49:29.807 position:19% line:83% align:start
it's where structures
called Substantia Nigra

00:49:29.841 --> 00:49:32.077 position:5% line:89% align:start
supply the brain with dopamine.

00:49:32.110 --> 00:49:34.880 position:7% line:83% align:start
People tend to think of human
will as singular and focused,

00:49:34.913 --> 00:49:36.747 position:7% line:89% align:start
like a soul with a conscience.

00:49:36.781 --> 00:49:38.816 position:19% line:83% align:start
You have an angel and
a devil on each shoulder,

00:49:38.849 --> 00:49:41.253 position:19% line:83% align:start
and the only choice is
between right or wrong.

00:49:41.286 --> 00:49:42.720 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
But, it's not that simple.

00:49:42.753 --> 00:49:44.189 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KEITA]
Not even remotely.

00:49:44.222 --> 00:49:46.891 position:13% line:83% align:start
Picture a crowded business
meeting with lots of individuals

00:49:46.925 --> 00:49:49.027 position:27% line:83% align:start
clamoring to get
their point across.

00:49:49.061 --> 00:49:51.729 position:10% line:83% align:start
The vast variety of desires
the brain experiences,

00:49:51.762 --> 00:49:53.497 position:10% line:89% align:start
function much the same way.

00:49:53.531 --> 00:49:55.666 position:21% line:83% align:start
They shout and kick,
or piss and moan,

00:49:55.700 --> 00:49:57.902 position:13% line:83% align:start
competing with each other
to get our attention.

00:49:57.935 --> 00:49:59.837 position:27% line:83% align:start
Out of all these
possible motivations,

00:49:59.870 --> 00:50:01.239 position:21% line:89% align:start
we only act on one.

00:50:01.273 --> 00:50:03.641 position:30% line:83% align:start
Deciding which
one is our will.

00:50:03.674 --> 00:50:05.943 position:16% line:83% align:start
But behind the decision,
our brain's reward center

00:50:05.977 --> 00:50:08.879 position:21% line:83% align:start
has trained us with
dopamine to respond.

00:50:08.913 --> 00:50:11.882 position:7% line:89% align:start
Like giving a treat to a dog.

00:50:11.916 --> 00:50:13.551 position:10% line:89% align:start
This fascinated your father.

00:50:13.584 --> 00:50:15.820 position:16% line:83% align:start
He became obsessed with
what might be possible

00:50:15.853 --> 00:50:20.158 position:7% line:83% align:start
if this chemical reward system
were artificially influenced.

00:50:20.192 --> 00:50:22.493 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
You mean mind control.

00:50:23.728 --> 00:50:24.829 position:35% line:89% align:start
Big shock.

00:50:24.862 --> 00:50:27.898 position:7% line:83% align:start
Had a feeling he had something
to do with the suicides.

00:50:27.932 --> 00:50:29.567 position:10% line:89% align:start
There's no evidence of that.

00:50:29.600 --> 00:50:30.801 position:16% line:89% align:start
And I'm rather surprised

00:50:30.835 --> 00:50:32.603 position:24% line:83% align:start
you could possibly
suspect your own father.

00:50:32.636 --> 00:50:34.805 position:27% line:83% align:start
He stopped being
my father years ago.

00:50:34.839 --> 00:50:35.940 position:16% line:89% align:start
As far as I'm concerned,

00:50:35.973 --> 00:50:39.211 position:13% line:83% align:start
I don't know who he is or
what he may be capable of.

00:50:40.945 --> 00:50:42.314 position:5% line:89% align:start
Don't be so quick to judge him.

00:50:42.347 --> 00:50:45.082 position:13% line:83% align:start
This is the science behind
the human soul itself.

00:50:45.116 --> 00:50:48.220 position:13% line:83% align:start
Many researchers have long
been tempted to pursue it.

00:50:48.253 --> 00:50:49.221 position:16% line:89% align:start
We only seek the truth.

00:50:49.254 --> 00:50:50.688 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm leaving for Baghdad,

00:50:50.721 --> 00:50:52.990 position:27% line:83% align:start
to ascertain the
whereabouts of Miach Mihie.

00:50:53.024 --> 00:50:54.658 position:7% line:89% align:start
I intend to find her remains,

00:50:54.692 --> 00:50:56.961 position:27% line:83% align:start
even if it means
confronting him.

00:51:02.367 --> 00:51:03.567 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Hm?

00:51:04.535 --> 00:51:07.038 position:21% line:83% align:start
[MAN] I can give you
a lift to the airport.

00:51:09.974 --> 00:51:11.942 position:21% line:89% align:start
Baghdad awaits, yes?

00:51:11.976 --> 00:51:14.812 position:21% line:83% align:start
That is classified.
And who are you?

00:51:14.845 --> 00:51:18.115 position:10% line:83% align:start
Since I'm in Isolation Mode,
allow me to introduce myself.

00:51:18.149 --> 00:51:22.620 position:16% line:83% align:start
Elijah Vashlov: Interpol
Special Investigator.

00:51:22.653 --> 00:51:24.855 position:7% line:89% align:start
Ever seen one of these before?

00:51:27.658 --> 00:51:28.626 position:38% line:89% align:start
A card?

00:51:28.659 --> 00:51:30.628 position:7% line:89% align:start
Aw, it's less fun if you know.

00:51:30.661 --> 00:51:32.263 position:19% line:83% align:start
Do you try to pick up
every woman you meet

00:51:32.296 --> 00:51:33.931 position:19% line:89% align:start
with a business card?

00:51:33.964 --> 00:51:36.600 position:10% line:89% align:start
It usually goes over better.

00:51:41.672 --> 00:51:43.240 position:35% line:83% align:start
[VASHLOV]
The whole country is scared.

00:51:43.274 --> 00:51:44.208 position:24% line:89% align:start
Things are quiet.

00:51:44.241 --> 00:51:47.144 position:21% line:83% align:start
Everyone's afraid of
what might happen next.

00:51:47.178 --> 00:51:48.145 position:21% line:89% align:start
Until the other day,

00:51:48.179 --> 00:51:51.749 position:19% line:83% align:start
almost no one had seen
death for themselves.

00:51:51.782 --> 00:51:54.085 position:10% line:83% align:start
They all assumed they would
never have to deal with it.

00:51:54.118 --> 00:51:55.786 position:24% line:83% align:start
People dying right
in front of you

00:51:55.820 --> 00:51:58.856 position:21% line:83% align:start
isn't something that
should happen anymore.

00:51:58.889 --> 00:52:02.726 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yet it did, and therapy
centers have reached capacity.

00:52:02.760 --> 00:52:05.396 position:10% line:83% align:start
Admedistration citizens were
happy in their ignorance,

00:52:05.429 --> 00:52:07.098 position:30% line:83% align:start
confident that
nothing unpleasant

00:52:07.131 --> 00:52:09.300 position:5% line:89% align:start
would ever knock on their doors.

00:52:09.333 --> 00:52:11.302 position:19% line:83% align:start
We are conditioned to
care for one another

00:52:11.335 --> 00:52:13.637 position:7% line:89% align:start
and protect life at all costs.

00:52:13.671 --> 00:52:16.040 position:21% line:83% align:start
That belief has kept
our society running.

00:52:16.073 --> 00:52:17.241 position:19% line:89% align:start
But now everyone knows

00:52:17.274 --> 00:52:20.845 position:13% line:83% align:start
this world has never been
the Utopia it appeared to be.

00:52:22.213 --> 00:52:24.248 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Does that frighten you?

00:52:24.281 --> 00:52:26.217 position:35% line:83% align:start
[VASHLOV]
Of course it does.

00:52:30.287 --> 00:52:32.056 position:27% line:83% align:start
Right now, most
people are terrified

00:52:32.089 --> 00:52:33.224 position:16% line:89% align:start
of what they don't know,

00:52:33.257 --> 00:52:35.092 position:30% line:83% align:start
while I'm more
afraid of what I do.

00:52:35.126 --> 00:52:38.162 position:13% line:83% align:start
The group Interpol's been
surveilling for instance.

00:52:38.195 --> 00:52:39.096 position:33% line:89% align:start
What group?

00:52:39.130 --> 00:52:41.065 position:24% line:83% align:start
A WatchMe research
consortium called the

00:52:41.098 --> 00:52:43.334 position:16% line:83% align:start
Next-Gen Human Behavior
Monitoring Group.

00:52:43.367 --> 00:52:46.170 position:10% line:83% align:start
My division has been keeping
an eye on it for a while.

00:52:46.203 --> 00:52:48.739 position:13% line:83% align:start
Amid all of the scientists
you would expect to find,

00:52:48.772 --> 00:52:50.307 position:21% line:83% align:start
are heads of medical
tech companies

00:52:50.341 --> 00:52:52.676 position:33% line:83% align:start
and powerful
Admedistration elders.

00:52:52.710 --> 00:52:55.779 position:19% line:83% align:start
Not exactly the lineup
of usual suspects.

00:52:55.813 --> 00:52:58.682 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's a long name for
a secret society.

00:52:58.716 --> 00:53:00.684 position:21% line:83% align:start
We're more concerned
with their ideology

00:53:00.718 --> 00:53:02.887 position:10% line:83% align:start
and why they've been trying
to fly under the radar.

00:53:02.920 --> 00:53:05.890 position:16% line:83% align:start
They seem to have strong
memories of the Maelstrom.

00:53:05.923 --> 00:53:08.225 position:24% line:83% align:start
Historians may not
agree on how it began,

00:53:08.259 --> 00:53:10.728 position:13% line:83% align:start
but there's no doubt about
how fast it went wrong.

00:53:10.761 --> 00:53:13.197 position:21% line:83% align:start
Humanity reverted to
savagery and barbarism

00:53:13.230 --> 00:53:15.698 position:16% line:89% align:start
in the blink of an eye.

00:53:15.732 --> 00:53:18.302 position:13% line:83% align:start
No one thought our species
was still capable of that.

00:53:18.335 --> 00:53:20.471 position:24% line:83% align:start
Not until several
millions of people died.

00:53:20.504 --> 00:53:22.406 position:24% line:83% align:start
So, now this group
wants to use WatchMe

00:53:22.439 --> 00:53:24.475 position:24% line:83% align:start
to ensure it never
happens again.

00:53:24.508 --> 00:53:27.178 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Hmph. That's quite
the conspiracy theory.

00:53:27.211 --> 00:53:29.146 position:24% line:83% align:start
What's the rest of
their evil plan?

00:53:29.180 --> 00:53:31.081 position:24% line:89% align:start
World domination?

00:53:31.115 --> 00:53:33.817 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'll speak slowly, since you
don't seem to understand

00:53:33.851 --> 00:53:35.019 position:19% line:89% align:start
what I am telling you.

00:53:35.052 --> 00:53:38.289 position:7% line:83% align:start
This one group has the entire
planet under observation.

00:53:38.322 --> 00:53:40.291 position:16% line:83% align:start
They don't trust people
to control themselves,

00:53:40.324 --> 00:53:42.092 position:24% line:83% align:start
so they exploited
a hole in WatchMe,

00:53:42.126 --> 00:53:43.894 position:24% line:83% align:start
which allows them
to manually override

00:53:43.928 --> 00:53:45.396 position:13% line:89% align:start
bad choices we might make.

00:53:45.429 --> 00:53:46.897 position:16% line:89% align:start
Take away our free will.

00:53:46.931 --> 00:53:48.132 position:38% line:89% align:start
Exactly.

00:53:48.165 --> 00:53:50.201 position:7% line:83% align:start
Interpol believed the suicides
that happened the other day

00:53:50.234 --> 00:53:52.203 position:24% line:89% align:start
were a first test.

00:53:52.236 --> 00:53:53.736 position:33% line:83% align:start
But, if they
created the override

00:53:53.770 --> 00:53:55.439 position:21% line:83% align:start
to keep people from
killing each other,

00:53:55.472 --> 00:53:58.242 position:19% line:83% align:start
why test it by making
them kill themselves?

00:54:04.048 --> 00:54:07.117 position:19% line:83% align:start
What would you say to
you and I joining forces?

00:54:07.151 --> 00:54:09.019 position:21% line:83% align:start
We both want to get
to the bottom of this

00:54:09.053 --> 00:54:10.487 position:24% line:83% align:start
and two heads are
better than one.

00:54:10.521 --> 00:54:12.755 position:21% line:83% align:start
Of course, Interpol
may take some convincing.

00:54:12.789 --> 00:54:14.391 position:21% line:83% align:start
Not everyone in the
office thinks highly

00:54:14.425 --> 00:54:15.459 position:21% line:89% align:start
of Helix Inspectors.

00:54:15.492 --> 00:54:18.329 position:19% line:83% align:start
They may not like one
horning in on their turf.

00:54:18.362 --> 00:54:20.964 position:24% line:83% align:start
Rumor has it, the
W.H.O.'s missions abroad

00:54:20.997 --> 00:54:23.234 position:13% line:83% align:start
aren't so much about peace
as they are about spreading

00:54:23.267 --> 00:54:24.934 position:16% line:89% align:start
the religion of Lifeism.

00:54:24.968 --> 00:54:27.837 position:13% line:83% align:start
And their non-interference
policy is bull.

00:54:27.870 --> 00:54:29.406 position:24% line:89% align:start
Well, that's true.

00:54:34.144 --> 00:54:36.413 position:19% line:83% align:start
[VASHLOV] Look, I know
a lot of this sounds crazy,

00:54:36.447 --> 00:54:39.450 position:5% line:83% align:start
but you have to believe me. Time
is short, and I need your hel--

00:54:39.483 --> 00:54:41.385 position:27% line:83% align:start
[VASHLOV gasps]
Vashlov, here.

00:54:41.418 --> 00:54:42.885 position:19% line:89% align:start
Turn on Edison Carter.

00:54:42.919 --> 00:54:43.920 position:33% line:89% align:start
Network 24.

00:54:43.953 --> 00:54:46.123 position:10% line:89% align:start
Some sort of breaking news.

00:54:46.156 --> 00:54:48.192 position:13% line:83% align:start
[CARTER] We interrupt your
regularly scheduled programming

00:54:48.225 --> 00:54:50.361 position:19% line:83% align:start
to bring you a special
report with new information

00:54:50.394 --> 00:54:52.263 position:19% line:89% align:start
on the mass suicides.

00:54:52.296 --> 00:54:54.498 position:16% line:83% align:start
Moments ago, our studio
received a memorycel

00:54:54.531 --> 00:54:56.799 position:16% line:83% align:start
containing an anonymous
message from persons

00:54:56.833 --> 00:54:58.034 position:10% line:89% align:start
claiming to be responsible.

00:54:58.067 --> 00:55:00.437 position:19% line:83% align:start
We will now play that
message in its entirety.

00:55:00.471 --> 00:55:03.006 position:7% line:89% align:start
Viewer discretion is advised.

00:55:08.945 --> 00:55:11.180 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ROBOTIC VOICE]
A lot of people have died.

00:55:11.215 --> 00:55:14.251 position:13% line:83% align:start
They all ended their lives
in the same moment.

00:55:14.285 --> 00:55:16.919 position:21% line:83% align:start
This must have been
shocking for you.

00:55:16.953 --> 00:55:19.989 position:16% line:83% align:start
Some of you experienced
the horror firsthand.

00:55:20.023 --> 00:55:23.192 position:24% line:83% align:start
And if you didn't,
you now fear that you will.

00:55:23.226 --> 00:55:26.330 position:5% line:89% align:start
We did this. We are responsible.

00:55:26.363 --> 00:55:31.000 position:13% line:83% align:start
How we did this, is for us
to know and you to find out.

00:55:31.034 --> 00:55:35.238 position:10% line:83% align:start
But you will. The weapon we
used is already inside you.

00:55:35.271 --> 00:55:38.041 position:21% line:83% align:start
You can't remove it,
it's too late.

00:55:38.074 --> 00:55:40.243 position:27% line:83% align:start
You've seen what
we are capable of.

00:55:40.276 --> 00:55:42.479 position:13% line:89% align:start
We have held you hostage.

00:55:42.513 --> 00:55:45.349 position:13% line:89% align:start
Are you frightened? Angry?

00:55:45.382 --> 00:55:48.985 position:16% line:83% align:start
You are probably feeling
several things all at once.

00:55:49.018 --> 00:55:50.987 position:16% line:89% align:start
Treasure these emotions.

00:55:51.020 --> 00:55:53.289 position:30% line:89% align:start
They are real.

00:55:53.323 --> 00:55:56.225 position:10% line:83% align:start
Yet, the society we live in
considers them dangerous,

00:55:56.259 --> 00:55:57.327 position:35% line:89% align:start
unhealthy.

00:55:57.360 --> 00:55:59.295 position:10% line:89% align:start
It doesn't want you to feel.

00:55:59.329 --> 00:56:01.432 position:30% line:83% align:start
We don't have
to stop feeling.

00:56:01.465 --> 00:56:03.066 position:10% line:89% align:start
This isn't written anywhere.

00:56:03.099 --> 00:56:07.003 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's not a law, but we are
compelled all the same.

00:56:07.036 --> 00:56:10.406 position:13% line:83% align:start
Haven't you had enough of
this constant, public coercion?

00:56:10.441 --> 00:56:14.344 position:13% line:89% align:start
Don't you want to escape?

00:56:14.377 --> 00:56:17.514 position:13% line:83% align:start
Let's make a declaration.
Right here, now,

00:56:17.548 --> 00:56:19.949 position:19% line:89% align:start
to create a new world.

00:56:19.982 --> 00:56:22.586 position:13% line:83% align:start
But, before we can embark
on this great endeavor,

00:56:22.619 --> 00:56:24.555 position:5% line:89% align:start
you have to prove you are ready.

00:56:24.588 --> 00:56:26.956 position:27% line:83% align:start
Sometime within
the next seven days,

00:56:26.989 --> 00:56:30.426 position:16% line:83% align:start
each of you must kill at
least one other person.

00:56:30.460 --> 00:56:34.430 position:16% line:83% align:start
Use any means necessary.
How you do it is not important.

00:56:34.464 --> 00:56:38.334 position:24% line:83% align:start
The only thing we
care about is why.

00:56:38.368 --> 00:56:40.503 position:5% line:89% align:start
Show us how selfish you can be.

00:56:40.536 --> 00:56:44.073 position:13% line:83% align:start
Demonstrate that you care
about self-preservation.

00:56:44.107 --> 00:56:46.643 position:13% line:83% align:start
Those unwilling or unable
to complete this task,

00:56:46.677 --> 00:56:49.212 position:13% line:89% align:start
will die. Simple as that.

00:56:49.245 --> 00:56:50.980 position:16% line:89% align:start
This is no empty threat.

00:56:51.013 --> 00:56:53.684 position:16% line:83% align:start
We will kill you without
warning and without mercy.

00:56:53.717 --> 00:56:55.451 position:24% line:83% align:start
All we have to do
is push a button,

00:56:55.485 --> 00:56:57.353 position:7% line:89% align:start
and you will kill yourselves.

00:56:57.387 --> 00:56:59.389 position:7% line:89% align:start
Don't believe us? Don't worry.

00:56:59.422 --> 00:57:01.491 position:27% line:83% align:start
We'll remove any
shadow of a doubt.

00:57:01.524 --> 00:57:04.227 position:21% line:83% align:start
This is real, and we
are very serious.

00:57:04.260 --> 00:57:05.161 position:30% line:89% align:start
Keep watching.

00:57:05.194 --> 00:57:07.029 position:13% line:89% align:start
It'll only take a moment.

00:57:07.063 --> 00:57:08.498 position:10% line:89% align:start
You don't want to miss this.

00:57:08.531 --> 00:57:10.566 position:5% line:89% align:start
We promise it won't disappoint.

00:57:10.600 --> 00:57:13.136 position:33% line:89% align:start
Stay tuned.

00:57:13.169 --> 00:57:14.971 position:27% line:89% align:start
[TUAN whimpers]

00:57:17.340 --> 00:57:20.510 position:5% line:83% align:start
That's all, and this station has
received no further messages.

00:57:20.543 --> 00:57:22.178 position:7% line:89% align:start
At the present time, however,

00:57:22.211 --> 00:57:25.081 position:16% line:83% align:start
we are unable to verify
the message's origin.

00:57:25.114 --> 00:57:26.349 position:21% line:89% align:start
Please remain calm.

00:57:26.382 --> 00:57:28.618 position:7% line:83% align:start
Until authorities are able to
authenticate these statements,

00:57:28.651 --> 00:57:30.953 position:13% line:89% align:start
there is no need to panic.

00:57:30.987 --> 00:57:34.123 position:24% line:83% align:start
--[VASHLOV gasps]
--[CARTER screams]

00:57:34.157 --> 00:57:37.293 position:24% line:89% align:start
[CARTER grunting]

00:57:37.326 --> 00:57:39.295 position:35% line:83% align:start
[VASHLOV]
What the hell did I just see?!

00:57:39.328 --> 00:57:40.696 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:57:40.730 --> 00:57:42.365 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's her!

00:57:43.366 --> 00:57:45.568 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
"Let's make a declaration."

00:57:45.601 --> 00:57:49.305 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's Miach. Those are her words!

00:57:58.581 --> 00:58:01.350 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
"The Sorrows of Young Werther."

00:58:01.384 --> 00:58:03.653 position:19% line:83% align:start
This book killed a lot
of people, you know.

00:58:03.686 --> 00:58:05.154 position:24% line:89% align:start
Rather impressive.

00:58:05.188 --> 00:58:06.189 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
It's just a book.

00:58:06.222 --> 00:58:07.690 position:16% line:89% align:start
How can it kill someone?

00:58:07.723 --> 00:58:09.325 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
Werther, the title character,

00:58:09.358 --> 00:58:11.394 position:21% line:83% align:start
falls in love with a
woman named Charlotte.

00:58:11.427 --> 00:58:14.697 position:13% line:83% align:start
But she is already engaged
to marry another man.

00:58:14.730 --> 00:58:17.166 position:27% line:83% align:start
This creates an
unfortunate love triangle,

00:58:17.200 --> 00:58:20.036 position:7% line:83% align:start
and when Werther realizes his
affections aren't returned,

00:58:20.069 --> 00:58:21.471 position:19% line:89% align:start
he takes his own life.

00:58:21.504 --> 00:58:23.539 position:21% line:83% align:start
Sounds like a tragic
love story, sure,

00:58:23.573 --> 00:58:25.608 position:19% line:83% align:start
but I still don't see
how it could kill.

00:58:25.641 --> 00:58:29.011 position:16% line:83% align:start
The book was so popular,
people tried to emulate Werther.

00:58:29.045 --> 00:58:30.613 position:19% line:83% align:start
They dressed like him,
ate like him,

00:58:30.646 --> 00:58:33.216 position:27% line:83% align:start
some even killed
themselves like him.

00:58:33.249 --> 00:58:34.250 position:19% line:89% align:start
Fiction is just that,

00:58:34.283 --> 00:58:37.186 position:21% line:83% align:start
but the emotions it
can elicit are very real.

00:58:37.220 --> 00:58:38.254 position:30% line:89% align:start
In this case,

00:58:38.287 --> 00:58:41.424 position:16% line:83% align:start
the power of suggestion
was strong enough to kill.

00:58:41.457 --> 00:58:43.359 position:16% line:89% align:start
I think that's amazing.

00:58:44.594 --> 00:58:46.562 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
What's wrong with me?

00:58:46.596 --> 00:58:49.398 position:19% line:89% align:start
Am I chasing a ghost?

00:58:58.608 --> 00:59:01.444 position:24% line:83% align:start
Cian was the only
one who got a call.

00:59:08.451 --> 00:59:10.686 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] I know whose
voice I'm expecting,

00:59:10.720 --> 00:59:13.489 position:7% line:89% align:start
but I don't wanna believe it.

00:59:13.523 --> 00:59:17.158 position:27% line:83% align:start
Cian did though,
even said her name.

00:59:24.700 --> 00:59:28.337 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
Hi, Cian, long time no speak.

00:59:28.371 --> 00:59:30.439 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm lonely. I miss you.

00:59:30.473 --> 00:59:32.575 position:33% line:83% align:start
You and Tuan
didn't come with me,

00:59:32.608 --> 00:59:35.711 position:27% line:83% align:start
even though you
promised me you would.

00:59:35.745 --> 00:59:37.513 position:19% line:89% align:start
You let me die alone.

00:59:37.547 --> 00:59:39.348 position:33% line:89% align:start
[TUAN gasps]

00:59:41.484 --> 00:59:43.352 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
I know it's been thirteen years,

00:59:43.386 --> 00:59:44.787 position:27% line:83% align:start
but I wanted to
get ahold of you,

00:59:44.820 --> 00:59:47.623 position:7% line:89% align:start
to talk about right and wrong.

00:59:50.493 --> 00:59:53.429 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
What do you think they are?

00:59:53.462 --> 00:59:55.665 position:21% line:83% align:start
Being a good person,
helping your fellow man:

00:59:55.698 --> 00:59:57.533 position:16% line:83% align:start
those things are right,
aren't they?

00:59:57.567 --> 01:00:01.236 position:19% line:83% align:start
Or, is it only because
society tells you they are?

01:00:01.269 --> 01:00:04.372 position:13% line:83% align:start
When push comes to shove,
right and wrong are just words.

01:00:04.407 --> 01:00:08.544 position:10% line:83% align:start
What matters is what you do,
how you act, what you believe.

01:00:08.578 --> 01:00:11.279 position:10% line:83% align:start
What matters is making sure
the world keeps spinning,

01:00:11.313 --> 01:00:12.715 position:10% line:89% align:start
making sure family goes on,

01:00:12.748 --> 01:00:15.317 position:24% line:83% align:start
happiness goes on,
peace goes on.

01:00:15.350 --> 01:00:18.688 position:19% line:83% align:start
Doing what needs to be
done to make life go on.

01:00:18.721 --> 01:00:22.357 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's what's right. Right?

01:00:22.390 --> 01:00:24.292 position:13% line:89% align:start
Except life doesn't go on.

01:00:24.326 --> 01:00:26.227 position:19% line:89% align:start
Nothing lasts forever.

01:00:26.261 --> 01:00:31.901 position:5% line:83% align:start
We're born, we grow up, we grow
old, we get sick... and we die.

01:00:31.934 --> 01:00:33.035 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's nature.

01:00:33.069 --> 01:00:37.138 position:16% line:83% align:start
And there is no right or
wrong in nature, only change.

01:00:37.172 --> 01:00:40.141 position:27% line:83% align:start
But, I guess...
things are different now.

01:00:40.175 --> 01:00:41.844 position:16% line:89% align:start
WatchMe changed nature.

01:00:41.877 --> 01:00:44.279 position:24% line:83% align:start
Illness and aging,
as the world once knew them,

01:00:44.312 --> 01:00:46.348 position:5% line:89% align:start
have been virtually eliminated.

01:00:46.381 --> 01:00:49.785 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well-being trumps all.
Health is the new god.

01:00:49.819 --> 01:00:51.020 position:24% line:89% align:start
In ancient times,

01:00:51.053 --> 01:00:54.356 position:10% line:83% align:start
kings and queens threatened
to execute any who opposed them.

01:00:54.389 --> 01:00:57.727 position:21% line:83% align:start
They ruled by force.
Might made right.

01:00:57.760 --> 01:01:01.162 position:5% line:83% align:start
Then, the Bastille fell and tea
was dumped in Boston Harbor,

01:01:01.196 --> 01:01:04.399 position:13% line:83% align:start
And "power of the people,"
became the order of the day.

01:01:06.201 --> 01:01:09.371 position:21% line:83% align:start
[MIACH] But, what if
people are the problem?

01:01:09.404 --> 01:01:12.775 position:21% line:83% align:start
How do we fight the
enemy within ourselves?

01:01:12.808 --> 01:01:15.577 position:19% line:83% align:start
When we let our bodies
decide what's right for us,

01:01:15.610 --> 01:01:18.480 position:21% line:83% align:start
the question and the
answer are both the same.

01:01:20.348 --> 01:01:22.217 position:21% line:83% align:start
You were supposed to
come with me, Cian.

01:01:22.250 --> 01:01:24.452 position:10% line:89% align:start
You and Tuan made a promise.

01:01:24.486 --> 01:01:25.888 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:01:29.892 --> 01:01:31.626 position:21% line:83% align:start
[MIACH] We swore we
were in this together.

01:01:31.660 --> 01:01:33.428 position:27% line:89% align:start
We made a pact.

01:01:33.461 --> 01:01:35.296 position:13% line:89% align:start
You hurt me, I was upset,

01:01:35.330 --> 01:01:37.833 position:19% line:83% align:start
but if you make it up
to me, I'll forgive you.

01:01:37.867 --> 01:01:39.501 position:7% line:89% align:start
There's still time to join me.

01:01:39.534 --> 01:01:42.805 position:10% line:83% align:start
Still time to show the world
nothing lasts forever.

01:01:42.838 --> 01:01:43.405 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:01:43.438 --> 01:01:44.406 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
Right here, now,

01:01:44.439 --> 01:01:47.776 position:16% line:83% align:start
prove your body belongs
to you and you alone.

01:01:47.810 --> 01:01:49.577 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:01:54.616 --> 01:01:56.584 position:21% line:83% align:start
--[TUAN whimpering]
--[MIACH] You control your body,

01:01:56.618 --> 01:02:00.455 position:16% line:83% align:start
It doesn't control you.
Be brave for me, Cian.

01:02:00.488 --> 01:02:02.323 position:16% line:89% align:start
Finish what you started.

01:02:02.357 --> 01:02:04.960 position:27% line:89% align:start
[TUAN whimpers]

01:02:04.994 --> 01:02:08.530 position:19% line:89% align:start
[TUAN gasps, whimpers]

01:02:08.563 --> 01:02:12.233 position:24% line:83% align:start
That's it. Show me
how strong you can be.

01:02:12.267 --> 01:02:14.202 position:19% line:89% align:start
Show it to the world.

01:02:15.637 --> 01:02:18.707 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

01:02:18.740 --> 01:02:21.376 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry, Miach.

01:02:23.745 --> 01:02:29.451 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

01:02:29.484 --> 01:02:30.952 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:02:30.986 --> 01:02:36.691 position:35% line:89% align:start
[coughing]

01:02:38.827 --> 01:02:40.962 position:10% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE ANNOUNCER] Northern
Passengers Flight 9-4-7

01:02:40.995 --> 01:02:44.365 position:10% line:83% align:start
from Tokyo will be arriving
soon in Baghdad Medical City.

01:02:44.399 --> 01:02:47.802 position:10% line:83% align:start
Passengers and flight crew,
please prepare for landing.

01:02:52.640 --> 01:02:55.043 position:24% line:89% align:start
Miach didn't die.

01:02:55.077 --> 01:02:57.779 position:30% line:89% align:start
She's alive...

01:02:57.812 --> 01:02:59.848 position:27% line:89% align:start
...She's alive.

01:03:04.686 --> 01:03:09.457 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Somehow, some way,
Miach Mihie survived.

01:03:09.491 --> 01:03:11.559 position:19% line:83% align:start
Now, she's reappeared
in dramatic fashion

01:03:11.593 --> 01:03:14.662 position:21% line:83% align:start
and thrown down the
gauntlet to the world.

01:03:14.696 --> 01:03:18.700 position:24% line:83% align:start
Kill and live, or
don't and be killed.

01:03:18.733 --> 01:03:20.802 position:10% line:89% align:start
This is her new declaration.

01:03:20.835 --> 01:03:23.905 position:7% line:89% align:start
Miach intends to test us all.

01:03:32.380 --> 01:03:34.549 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
The Dian Cecht Complex.

01:03:34.582 --> 01:03:37.085 position:21% line:83% align:start
After the Maelstrom,
Baghdad became a metropolis

01:03:37.118 --> 01:03:40.555 position:19% line:83% align:start
of teaching hospitals,
industrial medical centers,

01:03:40.588 --> 01:03:42.056 position:24% line:89% align:start
and research labs.

01:03:42.090 --> 01:03:44.993 position:27% line:83% align:start
Taxes were low.
Laws were lax.

01:03:45.026 --> 01:03:46.161 position:10% line:89% align:start
And the Admedistration here

01:03:46.194 --> 01:03:49.998 position:13% line:83% align:start
didn't ask what anyone was
doing behind closed doors.

01:03:50.031 --> 01:03:53.935 position:16% line:83% align:start
The perfect place for my
father to disappear to.

01:03:53.968 --> 01:03:56.304 position:10% line:89% align:start
And he took Miach with him.

01:04:04.045 --> 01:04:05.613 position:38% line:83% align:start
