one year from now.

01:05:24.759 --> 01:05:26.194 position:10% line:89% align:start
Which amount do you choose?

01:05:26.227 --> 01:05:28.029 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Probably the former.

01:05:28.062 --> 01:05:29.130 position:33% line:83% align:start
[GABRIELLE]
Most do.

01:05:29.163 --> 01:05:30.365 position:24% line:89% align:start
Given the choice,

01:05:30.397 --> 01:05:33.868 position:10% line:83% align:start
the majority of human beings
prefer instant gratification.

01:05:33.902 --> 01:05:37.005 position:13% line:83% align:start
But so do other primates,
birds, dogs, and cats.

01:05:37.038 --> 01:05:38.907 position:19% line:83% align:start
Organisms that exhibit
this behavior,

01:05:38.940 --> 01:05:42.110 position:19% line:83% align:start
