It's really you.

01:13:47.493 --> 01:13:50.028 position:21% line:83% align:start
How many years since
we last saw each other?

01:13:50.062 --> 01:13:52.131 position:33% line:89% align:start
Eight? Ten?

01:13:52.164 --> 01:13:54.400 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Thirteen, you bastard.

01:13:54.433 --> 01:13:58.203 position:10% line:83% align:start
You walked out on Mom and me
like we meant nothing to you.

01:13:58.237 --> 01:14:00.005 position:7% line:89% align:start
Of course you don't remember.

01:14:00.038 --> 01:14:01.673 position:30% line:89% align:start
Why would you?

01:14:01.707 --> 01:14:04.576 position:13% line:83% align:start
People all over the world
are killing themselves.

01:14:04.610 --> 01:14:06.545 position:38% line:83% align:start
[NUADA]
I've heard. It's unfortunate.

01:14:06.578 --> 01:14:08.280 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's unfortunate?!

01:14:08.313 --> 01:14:10.382 position:24% line:83% align:start
Is that really all
you have to say?!

01:14:10.416 --> 01:14:12.251 position:21% line:89% align:start
This is your fault!

01:14:14.486 --> 01:14:18.590 position:5% line:83% align:start
Pretty sure your friend, Miach,
deserves some of the blame.

01:14:18.624 --> 01:14:19.992 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:14:29.468 --> 01:14:32.204 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Why her? Why Miach?

01:14:32.237 --> 01:14:34.106 position:38% line:83% align:start
[NUADA]
Even before recent events,

01:14:34.139 --> 01:14:37.376 position:13% line:83% align:start
the teen suicide rate was
going up year after year.

01:14:37.409 --> 01:14:40.546 position:13% line:83% align:start
You tried it. Your friend,
Cian, considered it.

01:14:40.579 --> 01:14:43.015 position:24% line:83% align:start
Miach was ready to
go through with it.

01:14:43.048 --> 01:14:46.084 position:7% line:83% align:start
Many children rejected WatchMe
when it was first introduced

01:14:46.118 --> 01:14:48.620 position:19% line:83% align:start
and became determined
to hurt themselves.

01:14:48.654 --> 01:14:50.556 position:7% line:89% align:start
Lacking any kind of solution,

01:14:50.589 --> 01:14:52.224 position:5% line:89% align:start
all the Admedistration could do

01:14:52.257 --> 01:14:55.027 position:13% line:83% align:start
was round up the kids and
put them into treatment.

01:14:55.060 --> 01:14:57.262 position:24% line:83% align:start
The Next-Gen Human
Behavior Monitoring Group

01:14:57.296 --> 01:15:00.599 position:13% line:83% align:start
took custody of especially
resolute individuals

01:15:00.632 --> 01:15:02.701 position:10% line:89% align:start
who made multiple attempts.

01:15:02.734 --> 01:15:06.472 position:5% line:83% align:start
They were singled out to receive
an experimental treatment.

01:15:06.505 --> 01:15:07.673 position:16% line:89% align:start
We needed strong-willed

01:15:07.706 --> 01:15:10.409 position:16% line:83% align:start
guinea pigs to test the
Harmony Program on.

01:15:10.442 --> 01:15:13.345 position:16% line:83% align:start
Your friend, Miach, was
the perfect candidate.

01:15:16.482 --> 01:15:20.352 position:21% line:83% align:start
[gasps] What is this
"Harmony Program?"

01:15:20.385 --> 01:15:21.520 position:38% line:83% align:start
[NUADA]
Harmony.

01:15:21.553 --> 01:15:25.491 position:21% line:83% align:start
As in synchronicity,
order, coordination.

01:15:25.524 --> 01:15:29.361 position:10% line:83% align:start
Like musical notes blending
together to form a chord.

01:15:29.394 --> 01:15:30.796 position:13% line:89% align:start
Except what we were after,

01:15:30.829 --> 01:15:34.666 position:16% line:83% align:start
was a means to unify the
synapses in the human mind.

01:15:34.700 --> 01:15:36.401 position:10% line:89% align:start
The intent was to find a way

01:15:36.435 --> 01:15:39.371 position:21% line:83% align:start
to save mankind from
its own savagery.

01:15:39.404 --> 01:15:41.573 position:21% line:83% align:start
While working under
Professor Saeki,

01:15:41.607 --> 01:15:43.675 position:21% line:83% align:start
I began a thesis on
the brain mechanics

01:15:43.709 --> 01:15:46.578 position:5% line:89% align:start
behind choice and determination.

01:15:46.612 --> 01:15:49.046 position:16% line:83% align:start
When word of my research
came to the attention

01:15:49.080 --> 01:15:50.649 position:13% line:89% align:start
of certain top officials,

01:15:50.682 --> 01:15:52.651 position:21% line:83% align:start
who feared a repeat
of the Maelstrom,

01:15:52.684 --> 01:15:55.187 position:27% line:83% align:start
they asked me to
join their consortium.

01:15:57.422 --> 01:15:59.258 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's how it started.

01:15:59.291 --> 01:16:01.493 position:19% line:83% align:start
And eventually it led
to my choosing Miach,

01:16:01.527 --> 01:16:05.631 position:13% line:83% align:start
whose rejection of society
made her an ideal subject.

01:16:05.664 --> 01:16:07.566 position:19% line:83% align:start
I believed if we could
conquer her mind,

01:16:07.599 --> 01:16:10.669 position:16% line:83% align:start
somehow refocus it away
from its relentless pursuit

01:16:10.702 --> 01:16:11.870 position:24% line:89% align:start
of her own death,

01:16:11.904 --> 01:16:15.340 position:7% line:83% align:start
the program would be powerful
enough to control anyone.

01:16:18.477 --> 01:16:21.380 position:13% line:83% align:start
[NUADA chuckles] That was
the presumption, at least.

01:16:21.413 --> 01:16:23.415 position:7% line:89% align:start
Perhaps we over-simplified it.

01:16:23.448 --> 01:16:26.418 position:19% line:83% align:start
Anyway, welcome to my
humble abode. Come on in.

01:16:31.122 --> 01:16:33.559 position:24% line:83% align:start
Assume you're not
opposed to caffeine?

01:16:39.831 --> 01:16:42.768 position:13% line:89% align:start
You do your research here?

01:16:42.801 --> 01:16:44.201 position:38% line:83% align:start
[NUADA]
No, not here.

01:16:44.235 --> 01:16:48.172 position:19% line:83% align:start
Until recently, I had
a lab at Dian Cecht.

01:16:48.205 --> 01:16:50.107 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's where you took Miach?

01:16:52.411 --> 01:16:53.879 position:16% line:89% align:start
There were side-effects.

01:16:53.912 --> 01:16:55.279 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Huh?

01:16:56.448 --> 01:17:00.719 position:10% line:83% align:start
[NUADA] The Harmony Program
has one very serious flaw.

01:17:00.752 --> 01:17:02.888 position:24% line:83% align:start
In hindsight, the
result was obvious.

01:17:02.921 --> 01:17:06.592 position:16% line:83% align:start
We should've anticipated
what would happen,

01:17:06.625 --> 01:17:10.127 position:16% line:83% align:start
but we were on the verge
of a major breakthrough.

01:17:10.161 --> 01:17:12.698 position:16% line:83% align:start
We created a human mind
where the brain's entire

01:17:12.731 --> 01:17:17.536 position:13% line:83% align:start
feedback matrix worked in
perfect harmonious accord.

01:17:17.569 --> 01:17:21.873 position:19% line:83% align:start
However, Consciousness
...was destroyed.

01:17:21.907 --> 01:17:23.140 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:17:23.174 --> 01:17:24.576 position:13% line:89% align:start
Prior to testing on Miach,

01:17:24.610 --> 01:17:27.345 position:27% line:83% align:start
we were unaware
of this consequence.

01:17:27.378 --> 01:17:30.147 position:19% line:83% align:start
It wasn't detected in
any trials before hers.

01:17:30.181 --> 01:17:31.917 position:24% line:83% align:start
Can a person even
live like that?!

01:17:31.950 --> 01:17:33.919 position:19% line:83% align:start
So, what happened once
you were done with her?

01:17:33.952 --> 01:17:36.888 position:16% line:83% align:start
Did she end up drooling
in a wheelchair?

01:17:36.922 --> 01:17:41.425 position:19% line:83% align:start
No, nothing like that.
I'll try to explain.

01:17:41.459 --> 01:17:45.631 position:5% line:83% align:start
Going shopping, eating, living.
That goes on as usual.

01:17:45.664 --> 01:17:48.265 position:24% line:89% align:start
Just... no choice.

01:17:48.299 --> 01:17:49.467 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:17:51.870 --> 01:17:54.873 position:16% line:83% align:start
[NUADA] Decision making
is no longer necessary,

01:17:54.906 --> 01:17:58.409 position:13% line:83% align:start
because competing feedback
agents have been removed.

01:17:58.442 --> 01:18:00.746 position:24% line:83% align:start
From the outside,
it's impossible to tell

01:18:00.779 --> 01:18:01.713 position:19% line:89% align:start
who has consciousness,

01:18:01.747 --> 01:18:04.448 position:19% line:83% align:start
and who's simply going
through the motions.

01:18:04.482 --> 01:18:06.617 position:24% line:89% align:start
They act the same.

01:18:06.651 --> 01:18:08.586 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Did Miach?

01:18:08.619 --> 01:18:12.289 position:13% line:83% align:start
[NUADA] She appeared to be
living a typical, average life.

01:18:12.323 --> 01:18:15.861 position:10% line:83% align:start
She did homework, ate meals,
carried on conversations.

01:18:15.894 --> 01:18:16.995 position:19% line:83% align:start
When we first brought
her out of it,

01:18:17.029 --> 01:18:21.432 position:7% line:83% align:start
she described what she'd gone
through as pure ecstasy.

01:18:21.465 --> 01:18:23.701 position:16% line:83% align:start
After her consciousness
was restored,

01:18:23.734 --> 01:18:26.270 position:13% line:83% align:start
she couldn't remember any
details about what happened

01:18:26.303 --> 01:18:27.672 position:27% line:89% align:start
during the test.

01:18:29.340 --> 01:18:30.708 position:38% line:83% align:start
[NUADA]
Nevertheless,

01:18:30.741 --> 01:18:33.611 position:13% line:83% align:start
She recalled the sensation
of being in a blissful,

01:18:33.644 --> 01:18:34.612 position:33% line:89% align:start
happy place.

01:18:34.645 --> 01:18:37.815 position:16% line:83% align:start
She characterized it as
a positive experience.

01:18:40.518 --> 01:18:43.421 position:16% line:83% align:start
But, living without free
will is a kind of death.

01:18:43.454 --> 01:18:45.891 position:10% line:83% align:start
Given such serious concerns,
we thought the authorities

01:18:45.924 --> 01:18:49.860 position:19% line:83% align:start
should decide how best
to proceed, and they did.

01:18:49.895 --> 01:18:53.531 position:5% line:83% align:start
Using WatchMe, they uploaded the
Harmony Program to every man,

01:18:53.564 --> 01:18:56.300 position:10% line:83% align:start
woman, and child throughout
the Admedistration.

01:18:56.333 --> 01:19:00.404 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's in both you and me,
whether we like it or not.

01:19:00.438 --> 01:19:03.441 position:7% line:83% align:start
It's not activated, obviously,
but it's there in our brains

01:19:03.474 --> 01:19:08.245 position:19% line:83% align:start
as a safety mechanism
in case of emergency.

01:19:08.279 --> 01:19:10.381 position:24% line:83% align:start
If war and chaos,
like the Maelstrom,

01:19:10.414 --> 01:19:12.349 position:5% line:89% align:start
were to threaten mankind again,

01:19:12.383 --> 01:19:15.920 position:30% line:83% align:start
Harmony can be
turned on to stop it.

01:19:15.953 --> 01:19:17.755 position:30% line:89% align:start
No, that's...

01:19:17.788 --> 01:19:21.358 position:7% line:83% align:start
For the time being, at least,
it's going to stay off.

01:19:21.392 --> 01:19:25.930 position:10% line:83% align:start
Depriving humanity of their
souls, is a last resort.

01:19:25.963 --> 01:19:29.366 position:16% line:83% align:start
Though, some within the
organization disagree.

01:19:29.400 --> 01:19:32.803 position:16% line:83% align:start
They think we should be
using the program now.

01:19:32.837 --> 01:19:35.940 position:24% line:83% align:start
Of course they do.
Miach's one of them.

01:19:35.973 --> 01:19:38.275 position:24% line:89% align:start
[scooter rumbles]

01:19:42.813 --> 01:19:45.316 position:21% line:83% align:start
[NUADA] Miach is the
reason I asked you here.

01:19:45.349 --> 01:19:47.952 position:13% line:89% align:start
I need your help with her.

01:19:47.985 --> 01:19:49.787 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Do you, now?

01:19:49.820 --> 01:19:53.057 position:10% line:83% align:start
So you made a mess and want
me to clean up after you.

01:19:53.090 --> 01:19:55.493 position:5% line:89% align:start
You're just as selfish as ever.

01:19:59.029 --> 01:20:01.599 position:13% line:83% align:start
[NUADA] There's a splinter
group targeting me.

01:20:01.632 --> 01:20:04.902 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's not safe here,
you have to leave.

01:20:04.935 --> 01:20:06.437 position:33% line:89% align:start
Find Miach.

01:20:06.470 --> 01:20:07.671 position:19% line:89% align:start
She'll listen to you.

01:20:07.705 --> 01:20:09.974 position:21% line:83% align:start
You're the only one
who can stop her.

01:20:10.007 --> 01:20:12.643 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry to put this on you,
Tuan, It's the only way.

01:20:12.676 --> 01:20:13.844 position:38% line:89% align:start
Why me?

01:20:13.878 --> 01:20:17.715 position:10% line:83% align:start
You really think I'm the one
who's gonna save the world?

01:20:17.748 --> 01:20:18.916 position:41% line:89% align:start
I do.

01:20:20.551 --> 01:20:20.985 position:33% line:89% align:start
[shuffling]

01:20:21.018 --> 01:20:22.386 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:20:22.853 --> 01:20:25.055 position:30% line:83% align:start
--[TUAN] Dad!
--[NUADA grunts]

01:20:25.089 --> 01:20:27.691 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Dad, are you all right?!

01:20:27.725 --> 01:20:30.928 position:27% line:83% align:start
Elijah Vashlov:
Interpol Special Agent.

01:20:30.961 --> 01:20:33.330 position:27% line:83% align:start
So nice to meet
you, Dr. Kirie.

01:20:33.364 --> 01:20:34.632 position:7% line:89% align:start
I am placing you under arrest

01:20:34.665 --> 01:20:37.368 position:27% line:83% align:start
for collusion in
the mass suicides.

01:20:37.401 --> 01:20:40.571 position:13% line:83% align:start
Easy, Tuan! I wouldn't try
that again if I were you.

01:20:40.604 --> 01:20:43.507 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'll have you charged with
accessory after the fact.

01:20:43.541 --> 01:20:45.109 position:19% line:89% align:start
Cut the crap, Vashlov.

01:20:45.142 --> 01:20:47.812 position:16% line:83% align:start
I know you're conspiring
with Miach Mihie.

01:20:47.845 --> 01:20:50.815 position:38% line:83% align:start
[huffs]
Yes, typical Helix Inspector.

01:20:50.848 --> 01:20:52.883 position:27% line:83% align:start
You come up with
such wild theories.

01:20:52.917 --> 01:20:54.084 position:13% line:89% align:start
You tried to manipulate me

01:20:54.118 --> 01:20:56.352 position:21% line:83% align:start
to get to my father,
right from the start.

01:20:56.387 --> 01:20:57.555 position:33% line:89% align:start
I was bait.

01:20:57.588 --> 01:20:58.556 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's why you tipped me off

01:20:58.589 --> 01:21:01.425 position:24% line:83% align:start
about the Next-Gen
Behavior Monitoring Group.

01:21:01.458 --> 01:21:03.460 position:19% line:83% align:start
You knew if I started
asking about them,

01:21:03.494 --> 01:21:06.130 position:13% line:83% align:start
it'd get his attention and
he'd try to contact me.

01:21:06.163 --> 01:21:09.365 position:13% line:83% align:start
Nice work, inspector, and
since you figured it all out,

01:21:09.399 --> 01:21:10.301 position:21% line:89% align:start
what's my next move?

01:21:10.333 --> 01:21:13.504 position:16% line:83% align:start
--Kidnapping my father.
--[pots clanging]

01:21:13.537 --> 01:21:14.672 position:24% line:89% align:start
Ah, correct again.

01:21:14.705 --> 01:21:16.607 position:27% line:83% align:start
Your sweet papa
is coming with me.

01:21:16.640 --> 01:21:19.677 position:5% line:83% align:start
He's a key player in this game,
and he could ruin our plans.

01:21:19.710 --> 01:21:21.745 position:21% line:83% align:start
But, if I remove him
from the equation,

01:21:21.779 --> 01:21:24.548 position:7% line:83% align:start
then there will be nothing to
stand in the way of us getting--

01:21:24.582 --> 01:21:25.783 position:35% line:89% align:start
I was key.

01:21:25.816 --> 01:21:29.086 position:10% line:83% align:start
But, these days, I'm not as
important as you seem to think.

01:21:29.119 --> 01:21:31.789 position:24% line:83% align:start
Your false modesty
insults us both.

01:21:31.822 --> 01:21:34.091 position:19% line:83% align:start
You invented WatchMe,
you discovered Harmony,

01:21:34.124 --> 01:21:37.127 position:19% line:83% align:start
you are the mastermind
behind it all.

01:21:37.161 --> 01:21:39.529 position:27% line:83% align:start
And you're doing
this to get, what?

01:21:39.563 --> 01:21:41.932 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh, Tuan, don't tell
me you missed that.

01:21:41.966 --> 01:21:43.100 position:27% line:83% align:start
--[TUAN grunts]
--[VASHLOV yells]

01:21:43.133 --> 01:21:44.467 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Move it, Dad. Run!

01:21:44.500 --> 01:21:45.703 position:35% line:83% align:start
[VASHLOV]
What?!

01:21:50.608 --> 01:21:52.508 position:27% line:89% align:start
[VASHLOV huffs]

01:21:52.542 --> 01:21:53.878 position:27% line:89% align:start
[VASHLOV grunts]

01:21:59.449 --> 01:22:01.517 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:22:11.594 --> 01:22:12.763 position:30% line:89% align:start
[TUAN grunts]

01:22:16.200 --> 01:22:17.201 position:30% line:89% align:start
[NUADA yelps]

01:22:17.234 --> 01:22:18.903 position:30% line:83% align:start
[TUAN grunts]
You're hurt!

01:22:18.936 --> 01:22:20.670 position:38% line:83% align:start
[NUADA]
It's not bad!

01:22:21.537 --> 01:22:22.705 position:27% line:89% align:start
[VASHLOV grunts]

01:22:28.879 --> 01:22:30.047 position:33% line:89% align:start
[TUAN gasps]

01:22:32.116 --> 01:22:33.017 position:35% line:83% align:start
[VASHLOV]
Heh!

01:22:33.050 --> 01:22:34.051 position:38% line:83% align:start
[NUADA]
Tuan!

01:22:43.660 --> 01:22:46.163 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Dad, no! Why did you--?

01:22:48.765 --> 01:22:51.869 position:16% line:83% align:start
Pity. She told me not to
kill him unless I had to.

01:22:51.902 --> 01:22:53.770 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

01:22:53.803 --> 01:22:56.173 position:38% line:89% align:start
[coughs]

01:23:01.611 --> 01:23:03.680 position:30% line:89% align:start
[NUADA grunts]

01:23:03.713 --> 01:23:05.149 position:27% line:89% align:start
[TUAN whimpers]

01:23:05.182 --> 01:23:08.751 position:24% line:83% align:start
In the end, I got
to be the father...

01:23:08.785 --> 01:23:10.720 position:21% line:89% align:start
...I should've been.

01:23:16.193 --> 01:23:20.930 position:10% line:83% align:start
[VASHLOV] Without him, they
won't be able to stop it.

01:23:20.965 --> 01:23:25.568 position:16% line:83% align:start
He was the last voice of
reason anyone would listen to.

01:23:25.601 --> 01:23:28.972 position:5% line:89% align:start
All that's left, now, is chaos.

01:23:29.006 --> 01:23:33.676 position:13% line:83% align:start
The threats, the suicides,
just set things in motion.

01:23:33.710 --> 01:23:39.949 position:5% line:83% align:start
They were... catalysts meant to
cause a chain reactio-- [coughs]

01:23:41.851 --> 01:23:44.221 position:27% line:83% align:start
Tell me where to
find her, Vashlov.

01:23:44.254 --> 01:23:48.858 position:5% line:83% align:start
[VASHLOV] For a new world to be
born, the old one must burn.

01:23:48.891 --> 01:23:53.163 position:19% line:83% align:start
From the ashes of this
chaos, harmony will rise.

01:23:53.197 --> 01:23:55.999 position:19% line:83% align:start
Death and destruction
are means to an end.

01:23:56.032 --> 01:23:58.968 position:24% line:83% align:start
They are... first
steps on the path.

01:23:59.002 --> 01:24:03.740 position:13% line:83% align:start
Miach showed us the truth,
showed us the future.

01:24:03.773 --> 01:24:07.043 position:27% line:83% align:start
[VASHLOV gasps]
She will guide humanity

01:24:07.076 --> 01:24:12.849 position:7% line:83% align:start
to the promised land. [gasps]
If you want to find her,

01:24:12.882 --> 01:24:19.323 position:16% line:83% align:start
contact the Anti-Russian
Freedom Front, in Chechnya.

01:24:19.356 --> 01:24:23.960 position:16% line:83% align:start
She is there. [grunting]
You were once her friend.

01:24:23.993 --> 01:24:27.130 position:27% line:83% align:start
She said it was
okay to tell you.

01:24:27.163 --> 01:24:30.700 position:5% line:89% align:start
Don't make me suffer... anymore.

01:24:30.733 --> 01:24:37.006 position:21% line:83% align:start
It-It hurts! [gasps]
So this, this is pain.

01:24:37.040 --> 01:24:42.312 position:19% line:83% align:start
Thanks to WatchMe, and
MediCare, I've never known...

01:24:42.346 --> 01:24:49.619 position:5% line:83% align:start
...what it felt like. [panting]
Please... kill me...

01:24:53.222 --> 01:24:55.224 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gunshot]

01:25:08.971 --> 01:25:10.973 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
WatchMe began as a noble idea,

01:25:11.007 --> 01:25:13.910 position:16% line:83% align:start
then became law, and now
the very act of living

01:25:13.943 --> 01:25:16.779 position:27% line:83% align:start
is controlled by
the powers-that-be.

01:25:16.813 --> 01:25:20.116 position:7% line:83% align:start
But, "Death is power's limit,
the moment that escapes it.

01:25:20.149 --> 01:25:22.852 position:19% line:83% align:start
Death becomes the most
secret aspect of existence,

01:25:22.885 --> 01:25:24.320 position:24% line:89% align:start
the most private.

01:25:24.353 --> 01:25:27.790 position:7% line:83% align:start
Society's assigned itself the
task of administering life,

01:25:27.824 --> 01:25:30.827 position:21% line:83% align:start
but it cannot usurp
the power of death."

01:25:30.860 --> 01:25:33.096 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Who is it you're quoting today?

01:25:33.129 --> 01:25:35.098 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
Michel Foucault.

01:25:41.871 --> 01:25:43.339 position:30% line:83% align:start
Does that mean
there's no other way,

01:25:43.372 --> 01:25:45.775 position:19% line:83% align:start
and death is the only
way out of this?

01:25:46.742 --> 01:25:48.411 position:24% line:83% align:start
I lived somewhere
else when I was little.

01:25:48.444 --> 01:25:51.314 position:13% line:83% align:start
The people in charge there
did whatever they wanted to.

01:25:51.347 --> 01:25:53.249 position:16% line:89% align:start
It was a hell on earth.

01:25:53.282 --> 01:25:54.350 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Huh?

01:25:54.383 --> 01:25:57.053 position:16% line:83% align:start
You wouldn't believe me
if I told you what went on,

01:25:57.086 --> 01:25:59.322 position:7% line:89% align:start
but being here is just as bad.

01:25:59.355 --> 01:26:01.057 position:33% line:89% align:start
Bad as what?

01:26:03.192 --> 01:26:05.661 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MIACH]
The exact opposite of here.

01:26:05.695 --> 01:26:10.199 position:5% line:83% align:start
Things were so different there,
and yet, somehow the same.

01:26:10.233 --> 01:26:13.069 position:7% line:89% align:start
Over there, guns kill people.

01:26:13.102 --> 01:26:15.938 position:13% line:89% align:start
Over here, kindness does.

01:26:15.972 --> 01:26:18.040 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Even before that conversation,

01:26:18.074 --> 01:26:20.910 position:24% line:83% align:start
I suspected Miach
had a dark past.

01:26:20.943 --> 01:26:24.147 position:19% line:83% align:start
We spent so many hours
whispering at our desks,

01:26:24.180 --> 01:26:26.681 position:27% line:83% align:start
discussing plots
for mass murder.

01:26:26.716 --> 01:26:29.285 position:27% line:83% align:start
I knew there was
something behind it.

01:26:29.318 --> 01:26:32.822 position:19% line:83% align:start
Was she still carrying
around such hatred?

01:26:32.855 --> 01:26:37.026 position:7% line:83% align:start
Had it just grown and festered
over the last thirteen years?

01:26:37.059 --> 01:26:39.762 position:13% line:83% align:start
Was this happening because
she finally had the power

01:26:39.795 --> 01:26:42.899 position:21% line:83% align:start
to turn her macabre
fantasies into reality?

01:26:52.341 --> 01:27:01.350 position:27% line:89% align:start
[CROWD yelling]

01:27:17.832 --> 01:27:18.833 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gunshot]

01:28:19.228 --> 01:28:20.996 position:19% line:83% align:start
[OS CARA] The deadline
to kill or be killed

01:28:21.029 --> 01:28:23.932 position:13% line:89% align:start
is the day after tomorrow.

01:28:23.965 --> 01:28:25.534 position:24% line:83% align:start
Fear and trembling
have completely

01:28:25.568 --> 01:28:28.903 position:13% line:83% align:start
overwhelmed the masses and
things continue to get worse.

01:28:28.937 --> 01:28:32.475 position:7% line:83% align:start
Both the murder rate, and the
suicide rate are exploding.

01:28:32.508 --> 01:28:36.312 position:10% line:83% align:start
Combination murder-suicides
are at an all-time high!

01:28:36.345 --> 01:28:38.547 position:19% line:83% align:start
As of yet, no word of
violence or self-harm

01:28:38.581 --> 01:28:41.250 position:19% line:83% align:start
from within the police
ranks or military forces,

01:28:41.284 --> 01:28:42.951 position:24% line:83% align:start
But, I think those
reports are coming,

01:28:42.984 --> 01:28:45.388 position:30% line:83% align:start
and I won't be
surprised when they do.

01:28:45.421 --> 01:28:49.458 position:7% line:83% align:start
Might even be one of us Helix
Inspectors who cracks, perhaps.

01:28:49.492 --> 01:28:51.494 position:21% line:83% align:start
I know I don't have
to worry about you.

01:28:51.527 --> 01:28:53.496 position:7% line:89% align:start
You've already killed someone.

01:28:53.529 --> 01:28:55.331 position:16% line:89% align:start
It was in self-defense.

01:28:55.364 --> 01:28:58.033 position:5% line:83% align:start
[OS CARA] Then you don't have to
feel guilty about it. Lucky you.

01:28:58.066 --> 01:29:00.035 position:10% line:89% align:start
The man murdered my father.

01:29:00.068 --> 01:29:01.404 position:5% line:89% align:start
He claimed to be from Interpol,

01:29:01.437 --> 01:29:03.539 position:13% line:83% align:start
but I have since confirmed
he was a double-agent,

01:29:03.572 --> 01:29:05.608 position:33% line:83% align:start
who misused
classified intelligence

01:29:05.641 --> 01:29:07.242 position:19% line:89% align:start
to serve his own ends.

01:29:07.275 --> 01:29:09.844 position:21% line:83% align:start
The organization he
actually worked for is

01:29:09.878 --> 01:29:14.182 position:10% line:83% align:start
known as the "Next-Gen Human
Behavior Monitoring Group."

01:29:14.215 --> 01:29:16.385 position:24% line:83% align:start
They are a covert
research consortium,

01:29:16.419 --> 01:29:18.454 position:27% line:83% align:start
founded shortly
after the Maelstrom.

01:29:18.487 --> 01:29:20.955 position:16% line:83% align:start
From what I was able to
ascertain, their only objective

01:29:20.989 --> 01:29:23.892 position:5% line:83% align:start
is to prevent such an apocalypse
from ever happening again.

01:29:23.925 --> 01:29:25.160 position:24% line:89% align:start
For this purpose,

01:29:25.193 --> 01:29:29.264 position:5% line:83% align:start
They enlisted the aid of several
prominent neuroscience experts.

01:29:29.297 --> 01:29:30.899 position:13% line:89% align:start
My father was one of them,

01:29:30.932 --> 01:29:33.536 position:16% line:83% align:start
and I believe Gabrielle
Étaín is another.

01:29:33.569 --> 01:29:37.573 position:7% line:83% align:start
I suggest we bring her in for
questioning immediately.

01:29:37.606 --> 01:29:39.941 position:5% line:89% align:start
Ms. Étaín died. Three hours ago.

01:29:39.974 --> 01:29:41.042 position:33% line:89% align:start
[TUAN gasps]

01:29:41.076 --> 01:29:44.045 position:16% line:83% align:start
[OS CARA] Her death was
reported as a random murder,

01:29:44.079 --> 01:29:46.147 position:19% line:83% align:start
but if your suspicion
is correct, that could

01:29:46.181 --> 01:29:49.984 position:16% line:83% align:start
easily be a cover story
for an assassination.

01:29:50.018 --> 01:29:51.486 position:7% line:89% align:start
What is your current location?

01:29:51.520 --> 01:29:53.355 position:5% line:89% align:start
Right now, en route to Chechnya.

01:29:53.388 --> 01:29:54.022 position:35% line:83% align:start
[OS CARA]
Why?

01:29:54.055 --> 01:29:56.324 position:10% line:89% align:start
I don't wanna say too much,

01:29:58.526 --> 01:30:01.597 position:19% line:83% align:start
but there's a splinter
faction within the NGBMG.

01:30:01.630 --> 01:30:03.465 position:21% line:83% align:start
They pose a serious
security risk.

01:30:03.498 --> 01:30:06.167 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm concerned they may
have infiltrated the W.H.O.,

01:30:06.201 --> 01:30:08.671 position:21% line:83% align:start
as well as the Helix
Inspection Agency.

01:30:08.704 --> 01:30:09.904 position:35% line:83% align:start
[OS CARA]
Huh?

01:30:13.341 --> 01:30:15.543 position:30% line:83% align:start
We'll have to
continue this later.

01:30:15.577 --> 01:30:19.280 position:13% line:83% align:start
Everyone except Inspector
Kirie, please log off, now.

01:30:37.432 --> 01:30:39.934 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ELDER A] History seems
poised to repeat itself.

01:30:39.968 --> 01:30:42.370 position:19% line:83% align:start
We stand on the brink
of another Maelstrom.

01:30:42.404 --> 01:30:45.273 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ELDER B] Is this simply
the fate of humanity?

01:30:45.306 --> 01:30:47.542 position:16% line:83% align:start
To plunge into violence
over and over?

01:30:47.575 --> 01:30:49.477 position:5% line:89% align:start
After all we did to prevent it,

01:30:49.511 --> 01:30:53.148 position:24% line:83% align:start
how could this be
happening again?

01:30:53.181 --> 01:30:55.283 position:21% line:89% align:start
The Next-Gen Group.

01:30:55.316 --> 01:30:57.452 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ELDER C] Peace.
For over half a century,

01:30:57.485 --> 01:31:01.489 position:5% line:83% align:start
we carefully molded and crafted
a society to sustain it,

01:31:01.523 --> 01:31:04.692 position:19% line:83% align:start
but all we truly built
was a house of cards.

01:31:04.726 --> 01:31:06.661 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ELDER D] And now,
thanks to a few terrorists,

01:31:06.694 --> 01:31:08.496 position:24% line:83% align:start
it's about to come
crashing down.

01:31:08.530 --> 01:31:10.298 position:21% line:89% align:start
You know who we are.

01:31:10.331 --> 01:31:13.201 position:10% line:83% align:start
Assembled before you are the
members of a council responsible

01:31:13.234 --> 01:31:16.438 position:30% line:83% align:start
for protecting
humanity from itself.

01:31:16.471 --> 01:31:19.507 position:10% line:89% align:start
[gasps] So, it was all true.

01:31:19.541 --> 01:31:21.376 position:19% line:83% align:start
[OS CARA] Your father
was a respected member

01:31:21.409 --> 01:31:22.744 position:21% line:89% align:start
of our science team.

01:31:22.777 --> 01:31:27.115 position:19% line:83% align:start
His untimely death was
truly unfortunate.

01:31:27.148 --> 01:31:28.683 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ELDER E] When the rift
within our organization

01:31:28.716 --> 01:31:33.321 position:10% line:83% align:start
became a divide, Nuada Kirie
became a marked man.

01:31:33.354 --> 01:31:36.424 position:16% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] But he wasn't the
only one under surveillance.

01:31:36.458 --> 01:31:40.161 position:5% line:83% align:start
We were hoping Miach Mihie would
establish contact with you.

01:31:40.195 --> 01:31:42.564 position:10% line:83% align:start
Or, that somewhere over the
course of this investigation,

01:31:42.597 --> 01:31:43.731 position:21% line:89% align:start
you would find her.

01:31:43.765 --> 01:31:46.668 position:5% line:89% align:start
You and she were friends, once.

01:31:46.701 --> 01:31:50.472 position:7% line:83% align:start
Which explains why you gave me
five days without much fight.

01:31:50.505 --> 01:31:52.173 position:35% line:83% align:start
[ELDER A]
Despite being in hiding,

01:31:52.207 --> 01:31:55.109 position:7% line:83% align:start
Mihie and her accomplices have
still been able to hack into the

01:31:55.143 --> 01:31:59.681 position:7% line:83% align:start
brain feedback mechanisms of a
limited number of individuals.

01:31:59.714 --> 01:32:01.716 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ELDER B] They have the
means to control far fewer

01:32:01.749 --> 01:32:04.686 position:10% line:83% align:start
people than they claim, yet
they are using their power

01:32:04.719 --> 01:32:07.489 position:27% line:83% align:start
to incite chaos
throughout the world.

01:32:07.522 --> 01:32:11.593 position:7% line:83% align:start
What Miach Mihie wants, or why
she is doing this, unclear.

01:32:11.626 --> 01:32:13.394 position:10% line:89% align:start
Ours is a peaceful society,

01:32:13.428 --> 01:32:16.264 position:27% line:83% align:start
dedicated to the
preservation of life.

01:32:16.297 --> 01:32:18.700 position:24% line:83% align:start
Why would she want
to destroy that?

01:32:18.733 --> 01:32:22.203 position:19% line:89% align:start
What is her end game?

01:32:22.237 --> 01:32:24.405 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're one of the few
she's let get close to her.

01:32:24.439 --> 01:32:27.175 position:16% line:83% align:start
We need you to learn her
true motives, Inspector Kirie,

01:32:27.208 --> 01:32:28.776 position:30% line:89% align:start
and stop her.

01:32:32.112 --> 01:32:33.648 position:27% line:89% align:start
[TUAN chuckles]

01:32:33.681 --> 01:32:35.517 position:35% line:83% align:start
[OS CARA]
Find something funny?

01:32:35.550 --> 01:32:36.618 position:35% line:89% align:start
A little.

01:32:36.651 --> 01:32:40.120 position:16% line:83% align:start
You see, my father said
almost the exact same thing.

01:32:40.153 --> 01:32:42.457 position:16% line:89% align:start
So, If you don't mind...

01:32:42.490 --> 01:32:44.726 position:24% line:83% align:start
We don't have time
for this, Tuan!

01:32:46.561 --> 01:32:51.064 position:10% line:83% align:start
The fate of the entire world
rests on your shoulders.

01:32:51.098 --> 01:32:54.669 position:27% line:83% align:start
Then, I must be
pretty important.

01:32:54.702 --> 01:32:59.274 position:24% line:83% align:start
We are begging you
for your help, please.

01:32:59.307 --> 01:33:00.842 position:21% line:83% align:start
I don't give a damn
about helping you

01:33:00.875 --> 01:33:03.110 position:7% line:89% align:start
or saving your precious world.

01:33:03.143 --> 01:33:04.345 position:24% line:89% align:start
I will find Miach,

01:33:04.379 --> 01:33:07.582 position:10% line:83% align:start
but my reasons for doing so
are no one else's but my own.

01:33:07.615 --> 01:33:11.352 position:24% line:83% align:start
My father and Cian
Reikado are dead.

01:33:11.386 --> 01:33:16.624 position:7% line:83% align:start
She killed them. There's only
one thing I care about now.

01:33:16.658 --> 01:33:19.293 position:30% line:89% align:start
[grunts] Tuan!

01:33:19.326 --> 01:33:20.495 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:33:26.768 --> 01:33:30.103 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ELDERS] Life must be
preserved at all costs.

01:33:30.137 --> 01:33:35.275 position:21% line:83% align:start
But, is life without
a soul, truly life?

01:33:35.309 --> 01:33:37.812 position:27% line:83% align:start
There can be no
second Maelstrom.

01:33:37.845 --> 01:33:41.415 position:27% line:83% align:start
The world cannot
descend into chaos again.

01:33:41.449 --> 01:33:45.653 position:16% line:83% align:start
If mankind can no longer
repress its savage nature,

01:33:45.687 --> 01:33:49.256 position:21% line:83% align:start
we must activate the
plan of last resort.

01:34:01.703 --> 01:34:03.403 position:13% line:89% align:start
Give that to Miach Mihie.

01:34:03.437 --> 01:34:06.206 position:21% line:83% align:start
She'll know who it's
from and what it means.

01:34:09.911 --> 01:34:11.278 position:41% line:83% align:start
[UWE]
Dealing with the Anti-Russian

01:34:11.311 --> 01:34:13.313 position:16% line:89% align:start
Freedom Front now, huh?

01:34:13.347 --> 01:34:16.383 position:19% line:83% align:start
I brought the WarDog,
just like you asked me.

01:34:16.416 --> 01:34:18.318 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's fully equipped.

01:34:19.587 --> 01:34:21.455 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Thank you, Uwe.

01:34:29.697 --> 01:34:31.598 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] Back when we
were young and defiant,

01:34:31.633 --> 01:34:33.901 position:5% line:89% align:start
Miach and I agreed on something.

01:34:33.935 --> 01:34:37.805 position:10% line:83% align:start
We wanted a world without a
society that would stifle us.

01:34:37.839 --> 01:34:40.607 position:16% line:83% align:start
We wanted a world where
our bodies were our own,

01:34:40.641 --> 01:34:43.878 position:19% line:83% align:start
where we had more of a
choice in our own destinies.

01:34:43.911 --> 01:34:46.814 position:24% line:83% align:start
Why would she want
something so different now?

01:34:46.848 --> 01:34:50.250 position:5% line:83% align:start
Why would she want a world where
we ceased to be ourselves?

01:34:53.520 --> 01:34:55.355 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Coordinates.

01:34:55.389 --> 01:34:57.557 position:30% line:89% align:start
Huh, "Alone".

01:34:59.459 --> 01:35:01.829 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
That goes without saying, Miach.

01:35:01.863 --> 01:35:05.632 position:13% line:83% align:start
I've been alone ever since
the day I thought you died.

01:35:16.911 --> 01:35:18.745 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
Chechnya.

01:35:18.779 --> 01:35:21.715 position:7% line:89% align:start
The place where you were born.

01:35:21.748 --> 01:35:24.919 position:30% line:83% align:start
The place your
consciousness was born.

01:35:24.952 --> 01:35:27.821 position:19% line:83% align:start
You once described it
as a hell on Earth.

01:35:27.855 --> 01:35:28.855 position:38% line:83% align:start
[NUADA]
Decades ago,

01:35:28.890 --> 01:35:31.558 position:21% line:83% align:start
in the midst of the
Russian-Chechen conflict,

01:35:31.591 --> 01:35:34.761 position:10% line:83% align:start
an isolated ethnic minority
group was discovered.

01:35:34.795 --> 01:35:37.297 position:19% line:83% align:start
Anthropologists had no
official records of them.

01:35:37.330 --> 01:35:39.566 position:21% line:83% align:start
Their existence was
largely unknown.

01:35:39.599 --> 01:35:42.369 position:10% line:83% align:start
The mountain villages where
they lived were remote.

01:35:42.402 --> 01:35:44.237 position:5% line:89% align:start
In such a secluded environment,

01:35:44.271 --> 01:35:46.440 position:24% line:83% align:start
and having little
contact with outsiders,

01:35:46.473 --> 01:35:49.010 position:19% line:83% align:start
The people inbred over
many generations.

01:35:49.043 --> 01:35:51.778 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TUAN] What are you
trying to tell me, Dad?

01:35:51.812 --> 01:35:53.613 position:24% line:83% align:start
[NUADA] Because of
their pure bloodlines,

01:35:53.647 --> 01:35:55.315 position:30% line:83% align:start
the members of
this minority group

01:35:55.348 --> 01:35:57.718 position:21% line:83% align:start
all share a certain
recessive trait.

01:35:57.751 --> 01:36:00.454 position:7% line:83% align:start
Though this trait can be found
in the general population,

01:36:00.487 --> 01:36:03.523 position:21% line:83% align:start
the likelihood of it
occurring is extremely rare.

01:36:03.557 --> 01:36:06.027 position:16% line:83% align:start
The trait I'm referring
to is a chromosomal anomaly,

01:36:06.060 --> 01:36:09.529 position:5% line:83% align:start
which results in a missing gene.
The gene for the human soul.

01:36:09.563 --> 01:36:12.733 position:21% line:83% align:start
The gene in control
of consciousness.

01:36:12.766 --> 01:36:14.568 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TUAN]
So, these people's natural state

